《'''豪斯医生'''》（{{lang-en|''House''}}或''House, M.D.''）是一部[[美国电视|美国]]医务[[电视连续剧|电视连续剧]]，于2004年11月16日至2012年5月12日在[[福克斯广播公司|福克斯]]电视台首播，前后分为8季。节目主角是[[休·劳瑞|休·劳瑞]]饰演的[[格瑞利·豪斯|格瑞利·豪斯医生]]，为人特立独行且有些[[厌世|厌世]]和反社会倾-{向}-，医术高明的同时也严重依赖止痛药。豪斯带领一个[[诊断|诊断]]小组，在[[紐澤西州|紐澤西州]]一家名为普林斯顿一普兰斯堡（{{lang|en|Princeton–Plainsboro}}）的虚构[[教学医院|教学医院]]工作。这部电视剧的初始理念源于保罗·阿坦纳西奥，节目主创人大卫·肖则是创造豪斯一角的主要功臣。剧集的[[执行制片人|执行制片人]]包括肖、阿坦纳西奥和商业合作伙伴凯蒂·雅各布斯以及[[电影导演|电影导演]][[布莱恩·辛格|布莱恩·辛格]]，节目大部分镜头都是在[[洛杉矶|洛杉矶]]的{{link-en|世纪城|Century City, Los Angeles}}拍摄完成。

豪斯经常与包括自己诊断小组在内的其他医生发生冲突，因为他对病人病症提出的许多假设都是以微弱或存在争议的见解为基础。他经常无视医院的规章制度，导致与顶头上司，医院管理者兼医学院院长{{link-en|丽莎·卡蒂|Lisa Cuddy}}（{{lang|en|Lisa Cuddy}}，[[莉萨·埃德尔斯坦|莉萨·埃德尔斯坦]]饰）发生冲突。[[罗伯特·肖恩·莱纳德|罗伯特·肖恩·莱纳德]]扮演的[[肿瘤学|肿瘤科]]主任[[詹姆士·威尔森_(豪斯医生)|詹姆斯·威尔森]]是豪斯唯一真正的朋友。节目前三季中豪斯的诊断小组成员包括{{link-en|罗伯特·蔡斯|Robert Chase}}（{{lang|en|Robert Chase}}，[[杰西·斯宾塞|杰西·斯宾塞]]饰）、{{link-en|阿莉森·卡梅伦|Allison Cameron}}（{{lang|en|Allison Cameron}}，[[詹妮弗·莫里森|詹妮弗·莫里森]]饰）和{{link-en|埃里克·福尔曼|Eric Foreman}}（{{lang|en|Eric Foreman}}，[[奧馬爾·愛普斯|奧馬爾·愛普斯]]饰），但这个小组在[[豪斯医生_(第三季)|第三季]]结束时解散。第四季福尔曼重新加入了诊断小组，豪斯也逐步选择了三位新成员：[[蕾蜜·海德利|蕾蜜·“13”·海德利]]（[[奥利维亚·王尔德|奥利维亚·王尔德]]饰）、{{link-en|克里斯·陶柏|Chris Taub}}（{{lang|en|Chris Taub}}，[[彼得·雅各布森|彼得·雅各布森]]饰）和{{link-en|劳伦斯·库特纳|Lawrence Kutner (House)}}（{{lang|en|Lawrence Kutner}}，[[卡尔·潘|卡尔·潘]]饰）。库特纳在节目第五季还有过一次露面，之后再于第八季最后一集《[[人皆有死|人皆有死]]》再次出现。蔡斯和卡梅伦之后还有在节目中出现，不过到了第六季初，卡梅伦选择了离开医院，而蔡斯则回到了诊断小组。13在[[豪斯医生_(第七季)|第七季]]的大部分剧集中都没有出场，她的位置也由医科学生{{link-en|玛莎·麦斯特|Martha Masters (House)}}（{{lang|en|Martha M. Masters}}，爱波·塔布琳饰）取代。到了[[豪斯医生_(第八季)|第八季]]，卡蒂和麦斯特都离开了节目，福尔曼成为医学院新院长，{{link-en|杰西卡·亚当斯||Jessica Adams}}（{{lang|en|Jessica Adams}}，[[奥黛塔·安纳布尔|奥黛塔·安纳布尔]]饰）和{{link-en|朴琪|Chi Park}}（{{lang|en|Chi Park}}，查琳·易饰）加入了豪斯的诊断小组。

《豪斯医生》的[[豪斯医生_(第二季)|第二]]到第四季都是美国收视排列前十的节目，先后在66个国家和地区播映，是2008年世界上观众人数最多的电视节目<ref name="globalrating">{{cite web | work = The Huffington Post | accessdate = 2014-08-24 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140512232109/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2009/06/12/house-becomes-worlds-most_n_214704.html | url = http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2009/06/12/house-becomes-worlds-most_n_214704.html | title = 'House' Becomes World's Most Popular TV Show | first = Agence France Presse | last = Eurodata TV Worldwide | archivedate = 2014-05-12 | deadurl = no | date = 2009-07-13 }}</ref>。节目获得了多个奖项肯定，包括5座[[黄金时段艾美奖|黄金时段艾美奖]]、两座[[金球奖|金球奖]]、1座[[皮博迪奖|皮博迪奖]]和9座[[人民选择奖|人民选择奖]]。2012年2月8日，福克斯宣布当时正在播映的第八季将为节目划上句号<ref>{{cite web |url=http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2012/02/08/current-season-to-be-the-last-for-house/119252/ |title=Current Season to Be The Last for 'House' |last=Seidman |first=Robert |date=2012-02-08 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131117201451/http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2012/02/08/current-season-to-be-the-last-for-house/119252/ |accessdate=2014-08-24 |work=TV by the Numbers |archivedate=2013-11-17 }}</ref>。节目的最后一集于2012年5月21日播出。

== 制作 ==
=== 构想 ===
2004年，大卫·肖、保罗·阿坦纳西奥，以及阿坦纳西奥的商业合作伙伴凯蒂·雅各布斯一起-{向}-[[福克斯广播公司|福克斯]]提议制作一部《[[犯罪现场调查|犯罪现场调查]]》风格的医序侦探剧，这个时候节目的名称尚未敲定<ref name="macleans">{{cite web | last = Frum | first = Linda | title = Q&A with 'House' creator David Shore | work = Maclean's | publisher = Rogers Communications | date = 2006-03-14 | accessdate = 2014-03-20 | archivedate = 2013-04-03 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130403204600/http://www.macleans.ca/culture/entertainment/article.jsp?content=20060320_123370_123370 | url = http://www.macleans.ca/culture/entertainment/article.jsp?content=20060320_123370_123370 }}</ref>，医院中的大夫将会像侦探一样寻找病因<ref name="Housebuilt">{{cite journal | last = Gibson | first = Stacey | title = The House That Dave Built | url = http://www.magazine.utoronto.ca/cover-story/david-shore-house-creator-television-producers/ | journal = University of Toronto Magazine | publisher = University of Toronto | date = 2008-03 | accessdate = 2014-08-24 | archivedate = 2012-11-26 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121126125721/http://www.magazine.utoronto.ca/cover-story/david-shore-house-creator-television-producers/ }}</ref>。阿坦纳西奥看过[[耶鲁一纽黑文医院|耶鲁一纽黑文医院]]主治医师[[丽莎·桑德斯|丽莎·桑德斯]]（{{lang|en|Lisa Sanders}}）在《[[纽约时报杂志|纽约时报杂志]]》上的专栏《诊断》（{{lang|en|Diagnosis}}）后受到启发，打算制作一部医疗剧，剧中的普林斯顿一普兰斯堡教学医院就是以同为[[教学医院|教学医院]]的耶鲁一纽黑文医院为原型<ref name="Challen">{{cite book | author = Challen, Paul | title = The House that Hugh Laurie Built: An Unauthorized Biography and Episode Guide | publisher = ECW Press | year = 2007 | accessdate = 2014-08-24 | url = http://books.google.com.hk/books?id=uFdE9kXVgDkC&lpg=PP1&dq=The+House+That+Hugh+Laurie+Built:+An+Unauthorized+Biography+and+Episode+Guide&pg=PP1&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q&f=true | isbn = 1-55022-803-X | archive-date = 2014-08-26 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140826133756/http://books.google.com.hk/books?id=uFdE9kXVgDkC&lpg=PP1&dq=The+House+That+Hugh+Laurie+Built:+An+Unauthorized+Biography+and+Episode+Guide&pg=PP1&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q&f=true | dead-url = no }}</ref>{{rp|96}}。福克斯接受了提议，不过电视台当时的总裁盖尔·伯尔曼（{{lang|en|Gail Berman}}）告诉几位主创人员：“我想要部医疗剧，但不想看到白大褂从走廊经过”<ref name="M&Cjacobsinterview">{{cite news |url=http://www.monstersandcritics.com/smallscreen/features/article_1443308.php |publisher=Monsters and Critics |author=MacIntyre, April |date=2008-11-17 |title='House M.D.' interview: Katie Jacobs talks Cuddy, Cameron and House triangle |accessdate=2014-08-24 |archivedate=2014-05-17 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140517132408/http://www.monstersandcritics.com/smallscreen/features/article_1443308.php }}</ref>。雅各布斯曾表示，这一规定和其他多种因素一起，对节目的最终形式产生了重要影响<ref name="M&Cjacobsinterview" />。
{{Quote box|width=25em|align=left|quote=“我们知道电视台想要的是-{程}-序剧，而保罗想出的就是这么个感觉起来像警察-{程}-序剧的医疗剧方案。里面的犯罪嫌疑人就是病菌，但是，病菌并没有犯罪动机。”|source=大卫·肖，《作家行会》杂志<ref name="Challen" />{{rp|41}}}}
获福克斯认可后，节目获得的[[暂定名称|暂定名称]]是《追逐斑马，环绕枯竭》（{{lang|en|''Chasing Zebras, Circling the Drain''}}）<ref name="House-Holmes">{{cite news | title = House... and Holmes | date = 2006-01 | work = Radio Times | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110721055444/http://www.radiotimes.com/content/show-features/house/house-and-holmes-parallels/ | url = http://www.radiotimes.com/content/show-features/house/house-and-holmes-parallels/ | publisher = BBC Magazines Ltd. | page = 57 | archivedate = 2011-07-21 | deadurl = yes | accessdate = 2014-08-24 }}</ref>，这其中斑马（{{lang|en|Zebra}}）一词属医疗俚语，指的是不同寻常或是感觉情况模糊的诊断，而“环绕枯竭”则是指末期病例，病人的情况将无可逆转地恶化<ref name="fullhouse" />。节目起初的构想是由一组医生进行合作，试图“诊断那些无法确诊”的病例<ref name="The Concept">{{cite video | people = Jacobs, Katie; Laurie, Hugh; Shore, David; Singer, Bryan | title = House Season One, The Concept | medium = DVD | publisher = Universal Studios | year = 2005}}</ref>。肖认为，让剧中拥有一个比较有趣的核心人物是非常重要的事，这个人能够洞察病人的个人特点，并且通过发现他们的秘密和谎言来做出诊断<ref name="The Concept" />。随着肖和其他几位主创人员继续发掘人物可能的发展方-{向}-，节目的构想开始逐渐从-{程}-序剧改朝以主角为中心转移<ref name="Variety110eps">{{cite news | title = Fox's medical marvel stays on top | author = Werts, Diane | deadurl = no | url = http://variety.com/2009/scene/news/fox-s-medical-marvel-stays-on-top-1117999278/ | date = 2009-01-29 | work = Variety | accessdate = 2014-08-24 | archivedate = 2014-03-20 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140320120536/http://variety.com/2009/scene/news/fox-s-medical-marvel-stays-on-top-1117999278/ }}</ref>。这个人物之后命名为“豪斯”，这也成为节目的名称<ref name="House-Holmes" />。肖对剧中角色作了进一步发展，并亲自编写了《[[试播集_(豪斯医生)|试播集]]》的剧本<ref name="macleans" />。[[布莱恩·辛格|布莱恩·辛格]]是《试播集》的导演，还在主角演员的挑选中起到了重要作用，他曾表示：“试播集的片名是《人皆说谎》，这也是整个剧集的前提”<ref name="Variety110eps" />。肖还表示，1944至1994年间服务于《[[纽约客|纽约客]]》的作家[[伯顿·罗切|伯顿·罗切]]（{{lang|en|Berton Roueché}}）笔下许多耐人寻味的医疗案例对节目早期的多集节目剧情提供了灵感<ref name="Housebuilt" />。

肖在一家教学医院看病的经历成为他创作本剧的一个重要原因<ref name="EWinfo">{{cite news |url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,1043940,00.html |title=Dr. Feelbad |work=Entertainment Weekly |date=2005-04-08 |author=Jensen, Jeff |accessdate=2014-08-25 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140708103908/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0%2C%2C1043940%2C00.html |archivedate=2014-07-08 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。他在回首往事时表示：“我知道一出房门，他们就会毫不留情地嘲笑我（的无知），而我觉得，要是让一个（医生）角色在病人还没离开房间时就这样做，效果应该会很有意思。”<ref name="hulu-developing the concept">{{cite web | author = Shore, David | year = 2006 | url = http://www.hulu.com/watch/21606/house-house---developing-the-concept#s-p2-st-i1 | title = Developing The Concept | work = Hulu.com | publisher = The Paley Center for Media | accessdate = 2009-03-24 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090324225402/http://www.hulu.com/watch/21606/house-house---developing-the-concept#s-p2-st-i1 | archivedate = 2009-03-24 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。节目的一个核心前提就是主角在行动上有所不便<ref name="int-disability" />，剧组起初的构思是豪斯需要坐轮椅，但福克斯拒绝了这一思路。雅各布斯之后表示，自己很感激电视台坚持要求他们重新构想这个角色，他们一度给主角的脸加上疤痕，最后再决定为让豪斯的腿因误诊而受到严重伤害，不得不使用拐杖，并且还严重依赖[[麻醉药品|麻醉药品]]<ref name="Variety110eps" /><ref name="int-disability">{{cite web | author = Shore, David; Jacobs, Katie | year = 2006 | archivedate = 2013-06-17 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130617033642/http://www.hulu.com/watch/21680#s-p2-st-i1 | deadurl = yes | url = http://www.hulu.com/watch/21680#s-p2-st-i1 | title = House's Disability | work = Hulu.com | publisher = The Paley Center for Media | accessdate = 2014-03-20 }}</ref>。

==== 夏洛克·福尔摩斯的影响 ====
[[File:Sherlock_Holmes_-_The_Man_with_the_Twisted_Lip.jpg|thumb]]
[[格瑞利·豪斯|格瑞利·豪斯]]和[[阿瑟·柯南·道尔|阿瑟·柯南·道尔]]笔下的[[虚构人物|虚构]]侦探[[夏洛克·福尔摩斯|夏洛克·福尔摩斯]]存在许多相似之处<ref name="FactCheckEd">{{cite web | title = House and Holmes: A Guide to Deductive and Inductive Reasoning | archivedate = 2014-07-11 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140711145504/http://www.factchecked.org/Downloads/LessonPlans/DeductionInduction/teacher.handout.2.guide.to.clinic.scene.pdf | accessdate = 2014-08-24 | publisher = FactCheck | format = [[PDF|PDF]] | deadurl = yes | url = http://www.factchecked.org/Downloads/LessonPlans/DeductionInduction/teacher.handout.2.guide.to.clinic.scene.pdf }}</ref><ref name="EmmysHousecall">{{cite news | url = http://www.emmys.tv/events/2006/house-wrap.php | title = House Calls, ''An Evening with House'' | author = Slate, Libby | publisher = Academy of Television Arts and Sciences | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131227083156/http://www.emmys.tv/events/2009/hugh-laurie-and-cast-make-house-call | date = 2006-04-17 | accessdate = 2013-12-27 | archivedate = 2013-12-27 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。肖对此表示，他一直是福尔摩斯的粉丝，并且发现这个角色存在一个独特之处，那就是对客户比较冷淡<ref name="hulu-developing the concept" />。这些相似之处在豪斯对[[演绎推理|演绎推理]]和[[心理学|心理学]]方面的依赖上显而易见<ref name="FactCheckEd" />，有时这种依赖甚至看起来明显不合适<ref name="fullhouse">{{cite news |last=Jensen |first=Jeff |date=2007-04-06 |title=Full 'House' |work=Entertainment Weekly |pages=44–47 |url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,20016394,00.html |accessdate=2014-08-25 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140708120010/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0%2C%2C20016394%2C00.html |deadurl=no |archivedate=2014-07-08 }}</ref>，他还不愿意接受那些自己感觉无趣的病例<ref name="Season 1 DVD review">{{cite web | url = http://blogcritics.org/review-house-md-season-1-dvd/ | title = Review: ''House, M.D.'' Season 1 DVD | last = Wild | first = Diane Kristine | publisher = Blogcritics | date = 2005-09-02 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131111221703/http://blogcritics.org/review-house-md-season-1-dvd/ | deadurl = yes | accessdate = 2014-08-25 | archivedate = 2013-11-11 }}</ref>。豪斯的诊断方法是把一个个逻辑上不可能的诊断排除，福尔摩斯使用的也是类似方法<ref name="House-Holmes" />。两人都会[[乐器|乐器]]（豪斯会演奏[[钢琴|钢琴]]、[[吉他|吉他]]和[[口琴|口琴]]；福尔摩斯会拉[[小提琴|小提琴]]），都对药物有依赖性（豪斯吃[[维柯丁|维柯丁]]，福尔摩斯吸食[[可卡因|可卡因]]，不过后者只是为了消遣）<ref name="FactCheckEd" />。豪斯和[[詹姆士·威尔森_(豪斯医生)|詹姆斯·威尔森]]医生的关系与福尔摩斯和知己[[约翰·华生|约翰·华生]]的关系呼应<ref name="House-Holmes" />。诠释威尔森一角的[[罗伯特·肖恩·莱纳德|罗伯特·肖恩·莱纳德]]表示，自己的角色连名字都和华生相似，节目原本的设计是让豪斯与威尔森就像福尔摩斯和华生一样密切合作，在他看来，豪斯诊断小组的其他几位成员就代表着华生的角色<ref name="RSL">{{cite news | last = Ryan | first = Maureen | title = 'House'-a-palooza, part 2: Robert Sean Leonard | work = Chicago Tribune | date = 2006-05-01 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140708221512/http://featuresblogs.chicagotribune.com/entertainment_tv/2006/05/houseapalooza_p.html | url = http://featuresblogs.chicagotribune.com/entertainment_tv/2006/05/houseapalooza_p.html | accessdate = 2014-08-25 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-07-08 }}</ref>。此外，威尔森还有个可能已经去世的兄弟，就像华生酗酒成性而离世的兄弟一样（第一季第十集《不愿面对的过去》）。肖表示，豪斯的姓氏也意在对福尔摩斯表示一种微妙的敬意<ref name="House-Holmes" /><ref>{{cite news | first = Wendell | last = Wittler | title = Living in a 'House' built for one | url = http://www.today.com/id/7518037 | date = 2005-04-18 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131228032636/http://www.today.com/id/7518037 | work = msnbc.com | accessdate = 2014-08-25 | archivedate = 2013-12-28 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。豪斯的住址是贝克街221号{{lang|en|B}}，和[[贝克街221号B|福尔摩斯的住址]]完全相同<ref name="fullhouse" />。威尔森的地址也是221号{{lang|en|B}}<ref>{{cite episode | title = Hunting | series = House, M.D. | network = Fox Broadcasting Company | airdate = 2005-11-22}}</ref>。

多集电视剧中包含有关于夏洛克·福尔摩斯的喻指。《试播集》的主要病人名叫丽贝卡·阿德勒（{{lang|en|Rebecca Adler}}），这个名字源于首部福尔摩斯短篇故事《[[波希米亚丑闻|波希米亚丑闻]]》中的[[艾琳·艾德勒|艾琳·艾德勒]]<ref>{{cite news | title = Is there a Dr Watson in the House? | work = The Age | date = 2007-04-26 | first = Scott | last = Murray | page = 21 | quote = In the pilot, the patient is Rebecca Adler, named, no doubt, after Irene Adler. 'To Sherlock Holmes, she was always ''the'' woman,' as Dr. Watson so tenderly described her.}}</ref>。第二季的最后一集里，豪斯被一位发狂的枪手打伤，这位枪手姓“[[詹姆斯·莫里亚蒂教授|莫里亚蒂]]”，这也是福尔摩斯死敌的姓氏<ref>{{cite web | last = Wild | first = Diane Kristine | date = 2006-05-24 | title = TV Review: ''House'' Season Finale – "No Reason" | publisher = Blogcritics | accessdate = 2014-08-25 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140502001416/http://blogcritics.org/tv-review-house-season-finale-no/ | deadurl = yes | url = http://blogcritics.org/tv-review-house-season-finale-no/ | archivedate = 2014-05-02 }}</ref>。第四季的第10集《[[美妙谎言|美妙谎言]]》中，豪斯收到的[[圣诞节|圣诞礼物]]是《第二版柯南·道尔》<ref name="It's a Wonderful Lie">{{cite episode | title = It's a Wonderful Lie | series = House | credits = Writer: Davis, Pam. Director: Shakman, Matt | network = Fox | airdate = 2008-01-29 | season = 4 | number = 10}}</ref>。第五季第7集《[[发痒_(豪斯医生)|发痒]]》中，豪斯从一本柯南·道尔所著的《[[福尔摩斯回忆录|福尔摩斯回忆录]]》上拿出自己的[[钥匙|钥匙]]和维柯丁<ref name="The Itch">{{cite episode | title = The Itch (House) | series = House | credits = Writer: Blake, Peter. Director: Yaitanes, Greg | network = Fox | airdate = 2008-11-11 | season = 5 | number = 7}}</ref>；这季的第11集《[[给全世界的快乐|给全世界的快乐]]》中，豪斯试图利用一本由[[约瑟夫·贝尔|约瑟夫·贝尔]]（{{lang|en|Joseph Bell}}）编写的书来愚弄手下，而贝尔正是道尔创作夏洛克·福尔摩斯的灵感来源<ref name="House-Holmes" />。这本书是之前一年圣诞节时威尔森送的，后者还写下了“格雷格，让我想到了你”的字样。威尔森还在承认送过这本书给豪斯前告诉诊断小组的两位医生，这本书是一位名叫艾琳·艾德勒的病人送的<ref name="joytoworld">{{cite episode | title = Joy to the World | series = House | credits = Writer: Blake, Peter. Director: Straiton, David | network = Fox | airdate = 2008-12-09 | season = 5 | number = 11}}</ref>。《豪斯医生》的最后一集《[[人皆有死|人皆有死]]》是-{向}-1893年的《[[最后一案|最后一案]]》致敬，其中的情节暗示福尔摩斯很可能已经死去，柯南·道尔原计划以这个故事为福尔摩斯系列收尾<ref name="SepFinale">{{cite web | last = Sepinwall | first = Alan | date = 2012-05-22 | title = Series Finale Review: 'House'—'Everybody Dies': Keep Me in Your Heart for a While | publisher = HitFix | accessdate = 2014-08-25 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140223023243/http://www.hitfix.com/whats-alan-watching/series-finale-review-house-everybody-dies-keep-me-in-your-heart-for-a-while | archivedate = 2014-02-23 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.hitfix.com/whats-alan-watching/series-finale-review-house-everybody-dies-keep-me-in-your-heart-for-a-while }}</ref>。

=== 制作团队 ===
[[File:Bryan_Singer.2776_cropped.jpg|thumb]]执导了《豪斯医生》的《[[试播集_(豪斯医生)|试播集]]》和第三集《[[奥卡姆剃刀_(豪斯医生)|奥卡姆剃刀]]》<ref>{{cite web | archivedate = 2011-03-18 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110318190016/http://www.film.com/celebrities/bryan-singer/14644617 | title = Bryan Singer from House | url = http://www.film.com/celebrities/bryan-singer/14644617 | accessdate = 2011-03-18 | publisher = Film.com }}</ref>]]
《豪斯医生》由脚跟和脚趾影业（{{lang|en|Heel and Toe Films}}）、肖{{lang|en|Z}}制片（{{lang|en|Shore Z Productions}}）、[[布莱恩·辛格|坏蛋哈里制片]]与[[环球电视公司|环球电视公司]]一起为福克斯制作<ref name="Production info">{{cite news | url = http://www.thefutoncritic.com/news.aspx?id=20070718fox01 | title = ''House'' Announces Casting News | publisher = The Futon Critic | date = 2007-07-18 | accessdate = 2014-08-25}}</ref>。保罗·阿坦纳西奥、凯蒂·雅各布斯、大卫·肖、布莱恩·辛格分别是前三家制片公司的领导人，他们共同担任节目的[[执行制片人|执行制片人]]<ref name="EWinfo" />。劳伦斯·卡普罗（{{lang|en|Lawrence Kaplow}}）、[[彼得·布雷克|彼得·布雷克]]（{{lang|en|Peter Blake}}）和托马斯·{{lang|en|L}}·莫兰在《试播集》后开始成为第一季的编剧。另外几位编剧多丽丝·伊根（{{lang|en|Doris Egan}}）、萨拉·赫斯（{{lang|en|Sara Hess}}）、拉塞尔·弗伦德和加勒特·勒纳从第二季起加入。弗伦德和勒纳是商业上的合作伙伴，他们本可以在节目开播时加入，但谢绝了这次机会。之后看到节目获得了成功，两人才在雅各布斯再度邀请时同意加入<ref name="FinaleInterview">{{cite news | url = http://blogcritics.org/archives/2008/05/18/171211.php | title = House, MD Season Finale: A Conversation with Writers Garrett Lerner and Russel Friend | author = Barnett, Barbara | date = 2008-05-18 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090403164134/http://blogcritics.org/archives/2008/05/18/171211.php | publisher = Blogcritics | accessdate = 2009-04-03 | archivedate = 2009-04-03 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。[[伊莱·阿蒂|伊莱·阿蒂]]（{{lang|en|Eli Attie}}）和肖恩·怀特塞尔（{{lang|en|Sean Whitesell}}）从第四季开始成为节目编剧，莫兰、弗伦德和勒纳也从这季开始成为节目的执行制片人<ref name="Production info" />。[[休·劳瑞|休·劳瑞]]是节目第五季第二<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.film.com/tv/house/season-5-2008/episode-2-not-cancer/23307761 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090715213156/http://www.film.com/tv/house/season-5-2008/episode-2-not-cancer/23307761 | archivedate = 2009-07-15 | title = "Not Cancer" from Season 5 of House | accessdate = 2009-07-15 | publisher = Film.com }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://blogcritics.org/tv-review-house-md-not-cancer/ | title = TV Review: ''House, MD'' – "Not Cancer" | accessdate = 2014-08-25 | last = Barnett | first = Barbara | date = 2008-09-24 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140716140149/http://blogcritics.org/tv-review-house-md-not-cancer/ | publisher = Blogcritics | archivedate = 2014-07-16 }}</ref>和第三集的执行制片人<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.film.com/tv/house/season-5-2008/episode-3-adverse-events/23307894 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090416002705/http://www.film.com/tv/house/season-5-2008/episode-3-adverse-events/23307894 | archivedate = 2009-04-16 | title = "Adverse Events" from Season 5 of House | accessdate = 2009-04-16 | publisher = Film.com }}</ref>。

肖是《豪斯医生》的[[节目运作人|节目运作人]]<ref>{{cite web |via=HighBeam Business |deadurl=yes |url=http://business.highbeam.com/2012/article-1G1-145528030/shore-lands-2year-deal-nbc-uni |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5msffirZU?url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/hr/search/article_display.jsp?vnu_content_id=1002274628 |archivedate=2010-01-18 |title=Shore lands 2-yr. deal with NBC Uni |accessdate=2010-01-18 |author=Andreeva, Nellie |date=2006-03-30 |work=The Hollywood Reporter }}</ref>。到第6季结束时，贡献过节目的编剧已经超过24位，其中最多产的是为18集节目编剧的卡普罗，布雷克以17集紧随其后，接下来肖、弗伦德、勒纳均创作了16集，然后是莫兰（14集）和伊根（13集）。德兰·萨拉菲安（{{lang|en|Deran Sarafian}}）是前6季最多产的[[导演|导演]]，一共执导了22集，并且这其中没有第6季的作品，其次是导演了17集的格雷格·艾坦尼斯。此外前6季还有超过36位导演，其中大卫·斯崔顿（{{lang|en|David Straiton}}）单在第6季中就导演了10集，比其他任何导演都多。休·劳瑞则执导了第6季的第17集《[[封锁_(豪斯医生)|封锁]]》（{{lang|en|''Lockdown''}}）<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.film.com/tv/house/15039618 | title = ''House'' TV Show | accessdate = 2011-03-06 | publisher = Film.com | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110306125850/http://www.film.com/tv/house/15039618 | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2011-03-06 }}</ref>。伊兰·索尔兹（{{lang|en|Elan Soltes}}）从节目开始时就担任视觉特效总监<ref name="VFX">{{cite web | author = Bennett, Tara | url = http://www.awn.com/vfxworld/vfx-doctor-house | title = The VFX Doctor in the ''House'' | date = 2008-05-19 | accessdate = 2014-08-25 | work = VFX World | via = Animation World Network | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140825051757/http://www.awn.com/vfxworld/vfx-doctor-house | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-08-25 }}</ref>。耶鲁一纽黑文医院助理临床医学教授丽莎·桑德斯是节目的技术顾问，她在《纽约时报杂志》上的专栏《诊断》是《豪斯医生》最初的灵感来源<ref>{{cite news | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110929143015/http://yalemedicine.yale.edu/ym_sp08/alumni_faces.html | archivedate = 2011-09-29 | url = http://yalemedicine.yale.edu/ym_sp08/alumni_faces.html | title = A doctor's passion for medical storytelling | author = Max, Jill | publisher = Yale Medicine Magazine | date = 2008-05 | accessdate = 2011-09-29 }}</ref>。据肖的说法，一共有“三位不同的医生……检查我们做的每一件事”<ref name="ET">{{cite web | author = Staff | title = Behind The Scenes At "House" | url = http://www.etonline.com/tv/2006/01/35979/index.html | work = Entertainment Tonight | publisher = CBS Studios Inc. | date = 2006-01-29 | accessdate = 2008-07-10 | archivedate = 2008-07-10 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080710072927/http://www.etonline.com/tv/2006/01/35979/index.html }}</ref>。拥有[[护士|护士]]执照的伯宾·伯格斯通（{{lang|en|Bobbin Bergstrom}}）是节目的片场医疗顾问<ref name="ET" />。

=== 演员选择 ===
{{Quote box|width=25em|align=left|quote=“对我来说，最初考虑（出演《豪斯医生》）并不是个很大的决定。因为大部分情况下节目在试播后还会继续的只有很少一部分，只有约四分之一会播到第二年。所以那时我以为这大概也就是三个礼拜的事，做梦也没想到三年半后自己还在演这个节目。”|source=[[休·劳瑞|休·劳瑞]]<ref>{{cite news |title=Man about the House |author=Clune, Richard |work=The Daily Telegraph |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090401170200/http://www.news.com.au/dailytelegraph/story/0%2C22049%2C22657520-5009160%2C00.html |url=http://www.news.com.au/dailytelegraph/story/0,22049,22657520-5009160,00.html |date=2007-10-28 |accessdate=2009-04-01 |archivedate=2009-04-01 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>}}
制片人起初打算找一位“典型的美国人”来扮演豪斯一角<ref name="lauriegetshouse" />，特别是布莱恩·辛格表示自己看到很多外国演员前来试镜后，心里越来越觉得非美国人不可<ref name="The Concept" />。休·劳瑞于本剧选角期间正在参加电影《[[凤凰劫_(2004年电影)|凤凰劫]]》（{{lang|en|''Flight of the Phoenix''}}）的拍摄，他在[[纳米比亚|纳米比亚]]一间酒店的浴室拍了试镜录像带，这是他在当地唯一能找到充足光线的地方<ref name="lauriegetshouse">{{cite news | author = Keveney, Bill | date = 2004-11-16 | title = Hugh Laurie gets into 'House' | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131222024905/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/television/news/2004-11-15-hugh-laurie_x.htm | url = http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/television/news/2004-11-15-hugh-laurie_x.htm | work = USA Today | accessdate = 2014-08-25 | archivedate = 2013-12-22 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。他在视频中对自己的形象和镜头里的环境致歉<ref name="Casting">{{cite video | people = Laurie, Hugh | title = House Season One, Casting Session with Hugh Laurie | medium = DVD | publisher = Universal Studios | year = 2004}}</ref>，辛格则觉得这段视频看上去和“[[奥萨马·本·拉登|本·拉登]]的视频”有得一比<ref name="torontosun-laurie">{{cite news | author = Brioux, Bill | date = 2004-11-14 | title = Compelling 'House' Doctor | work = The Toronto Sun | page = TV2}}</ref>。劳瑞现场即兴发挥，用一把[[雨伞|雨伞]]充当拐杖<ref name="BTVLaurie">{{cite news | url = http://www.buddytv.com/articles/house/how-hugh-laurie-got-into-house-20722.aspx | title = How Hugh Laurie Got into 'House' | publisher = BuddyTV | date = 2008-06-24 | author = DeLeon, Kris | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121019154810/http://www.buddytv.com/articles/house/how-hugh-laurie-got-into-house-20722.aspx | archivedate = 2012-10-19 | deadurl = yes | accessdate = 2014-03-20 }}</ref>。辛格对男演员的表现留下了深刻印象，之后还称赞这位“美国演员”是如何准确地把握了人物特点<ref name="The Concept" />，并且劳瑞唯妙唯肖的[[美国英语|美国口音]]也让辛格完全没想到他其实是英国人。劳瑞则把这种口音“归功”于自己小时候把太多时间花在看电视和电影上<ref name="lauriegetshouse" />。虽然当时主创人员还考虑过[[丹尼斯·利瑞|丹尼斯·利瑞]]（{{lang|en|Denis Leary}}）、[[大卫·克罗斯|大卫·克罗斯]]（{{lang|en|David Cross}}）、[[罗伯·莫洛|罗伯·莫洛]]（{{lang|en|Rob Morrow}}）和[[帕特里克·德姆西|帕特里克·德姆西]]这几位在美国更具知名度的演员，但肖、雅各布斯和阿坦纳西奥都像辛格一样对劳瑞的表现留下深刻印象，因此决定由他来饰演男主角<ref name="Challen" />{{rp|39}}。

劳瑞之后透露，自己起初以为节目的核心人物是詹姆斯·威尔森医生，豪斯不过是个“陪衬”，直到拿到《试播集》的全本剧本后才意识到原来自己获演的是主角<ref name="Inside">{{cite episode | title = Hugh Laurie Interview | series = Inside the Actor's Studio | network = BRAVO Network | airdate = 2006-07-31 | season = 12 | number = 189}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.usmagazine.com/houses_hugh_laurie_battling_minor_depression | title = House's Hugh Laurie Battling "Mild Depression" | work = Us Weekly | date = 2007-12-30 | author = Cina, Mark | accessdate = 2009-05-15 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090515113720/http://www.usmagazine.com/houses_hugh_laurie_battling_minor_depression | archivedate = 2009-05-15 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。由于父亲[[冉·劳瑞|冉·劳瑞]]（{{lang|en|Ran Laurie}}）就是名医生，劳瑞表示对自己“变成父亲的假冒版本”，但获得的酬劳却更高感到愧疚<ref name="lauriegetshouse" />。从第三季开始，他每集可以获得27.5万到30万美元的报酬，相当于他刚出演该剧时片酬的三倍<ref>{{cite web |archivedate=2014-03-31 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140331070630/http://www.zap2it.com/tv/news/zap-hughlauriehouseraise%2C0%2C7642764.story |url=http://www.zap2it.com/tv/news/zap-hughlauriehouseraise,0,7642764.story |title=Raise Prescribed for 'House' Star |publisher=Zap2it |date=2008-02-23 |accessdate=2014-03-31 }}</ref><ref name="Dailymail">{{cite news | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140118190540/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/femail/article-1042886/Is-Hugh-Laurie-new-George-Clooney-The-House-actor-hes-set-pulses-racing-TVs-moodiest-medic.html | archivedate = 2014-01-18 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.dailymail.co.uk/femail/article-1042886/Is-Hugh-Laurie-new-George-Clooney-The-House-actor-hes-set-pulses-racing-TVs-moodiest-medic.html | title = Is Hugh Laurie the new George Clooney? The House actor on how he's set pulses racing as TV's moodiest medic | author = Donnelly, Gabrielle | date = 2008-08-09 | work = Daily Mail | accessdate = 2014-08-25 }}</ref>。到节目第五季时，劳瑞出演每集的收入已有约40万美元，成为片酬最高的电视演员之一<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.tvguide.com/news/Houses-Hugh-Laurie-17540.aspx | title = House's Hugh Laurie Gets Huge Raise | work = TV Guide | last = Fox | first = Erin | date = 2008-09-12 | accessdate = 2014-08-25 | archivedate = 2014-08-06 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140806094037/http://www.tvguide.com/news/Houses-Hugh-Laurie-17540.aspx | deadurl = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.hellomagazine.com/film/2008/09/13/hugh-laurie-house/ | title = New ￡5 million contract is sweet medicine for House's Hugh Laurie | publisher = HelloMagazine.com | date = 2008-09-13 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130729082826/http://www.hellomagazine.com/film/2008/09/13/hugh-laurie-house/ | accessdate = 2014-08-25 | archivedate = 2013-07-29 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。
[[File:Hugh_Laurie_2009_crop.jpg|thumb]]在[[纳米比亚|纳米比亚]]拍摄一部电影期间制作了自己试镜的录像带]]

罗伯特·肖恩·莱纳德在同一时期收到了《豪斯医生》和{{lang|en|[[CBS_(电视网)|CBS]]}}电视网节目《[[数字追凶|数字追凶]]》的剧本<ref name="EWleonard" />，他觉得《数字追凶》的脚本“挺酷”并已计划参加试镜<ref name="EWleonard" />。但是，他觉得自己在该剧中的角色[[查理·艾普斯|查理·艾普斯]]（{{lang|en|Charlie Eppes}}）戏份太多，之后莱纳德表示：“我干活越少就越开心”<ref name="EWleonard">{{cite web |author=Wolk, Josh |date=2007-07-03 |archivedate=2013-12-11 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131211073123/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0%2C%2C20044586%2C00.html |url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,20044586,00.html |title=A Summer Away from the 'House' |work=Entertainment Weekly |accessdate=2014-03-20 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。莱纳德觉得自己试镜时表现欠差，不过由于他和辛格是老朋友，所以最后还是得到了这个角色<ref name="EWleonard" />。辛格对[[莉萨·埃德尔斯坦|莉萨·埃德尔斯坦]]在《[[白宫风云|白宫风云]]》中出演的妓女留下了深刻印象，所以寄了试播集的剧本给她<ref name="Challen" />{{rp|65}}。埃德尔斯坦对剧本的品质感到满意，特别是丽莎·卡迪医生和豪斯之间“火爆的对话”，她之后获选出演这个角色<ref name="Challen" />{{rp|65}}。

[[澳大利亚|澳大利亚]]男演员[[杰西·斯宾塞|杰西·斯宾塞]]的经济人建议他参加罗伯特·蔡斯一角试镜，但他对此有些拿不定主意，担心节目和《[[综合医院|综合医院]]》（{{lang|en|''General Hospital''}}）这样的[[肥皂剧|肥皂剧]]雷同，但看到剧本后就改变了主意<ref>{{cite news |author=Staff |date=2007-09-17 |deadurl=yes |archivedate=2012-02-24 |work=The Star |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120224235743/http://ecentral.my/news/story.asp?file=%2F2007%2F9%2F17%2Ftvnradio%2F18869314&sec=tvnradio |url=http://www.star-ecentral.com/news/story.asp?file=/2007/9/17/tvnradio/18869314&sec=tvnradio |title=Doctor in the house |accessdate=2012-02-24 }}</ref>。获选出演后，他开始努力说服制片人把这个角色改写成澳大利亚人<ref>{{cite news |author=Marquand, Sarrah |date=2006-10-04 |url=http://www.news.com.au/couriermail/story/0,23739,20517580-5003422,00.html |title=Young doctor |work=The Courier-Mail |accessdate=2008-09-27 |archivedate=2010-02-01 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100201051537/http://www.news.com.au/couriermail/story/0%2C23739%2C20517580-5003422%2C00.html }}</ref>。帕特里克·德姆西也参加了蔡斯一角的试镜，他之后因出演《[[实习医生格蕾|实习医生格蕾]]》中的德里克·谢柏德（{{lang|en|Derek Shepherd}}）医生而为人所知<ref>{{cite news | title = Actress makes 'House' call | author = Elfman, Doug | work = Buffalo Grove Countryside | date = 2006-04-20}}</ref>。诠释埃里克·福尔曼一角的欧玛·艾普斯之前曾在[[全国广播公司|全国广播公司]]医务剧《[[急诊室的故事|急诊室的故事]]》里出演一位陷入困境的实习医生，这段经历对他在本剧的演出产生了影响<ref>{{cite web | author =  | date = 2007-10-11 | url = http://television.aol.com/tv-celebrity-interviews/omar-epps | title = Omar Epps Is Back in the 'House'! | publisher = AOL-Time Warner | accessdate = 2008-09-28 | archivedate = 2007-08-19 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20070819092237/http://television.aol.com/tv-celebrity-interviews/omar-epps }}</ref>。[[詹妮弗·莫里森|詹妮弗·莫里森]]觉得自己在阿莉森·卡梅伦医生一角试镜时的表现完全就是场灾难<ref name="Challen" />{{rp|83}}，不过辛格在此前就看过她包括《[[恋爱时代_(美国电视剧)|恋爱时代]]》在内的一些演出，已经打算请她出演这个角色<ref name="Challen" />{{rp|83}}。莫里森的角色在第六季期间离开了医院，她也离开了这个节目<ref>{{cite news | url = http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/showtracker/2009/09/actress-jennifer-morrison-to-exit-house.html | title = Actress Jennifer Morrison to exit 'House' | accessdate = 2014-08-25 | last = Martin | first = Denise | date = 2009-09-24 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140809214819/http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/showtracker/2009/09/actress-jennifer-morrison-to-exit-house.html | archivedate = 2014-08-09 | deadurl = no | work = Los Angeles Times }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131105191215/http://insidetv.ew.com/2009/09/24/exclusive-jennifer-morrison-leaving-house/ | url = http://insidetv.ew.com/2009/09/24/exclusive-jennifer-morrison-leaving-house/ | title = Exclusive: Jennifer Morrison leaving 'House' | accessdate = 2014-08-25 | last = Ausiello | first = Michael | date = 2009-09-24 | work = Entertainment Weekly | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2013-11-05 }}</ref>。

豪斯在第三季结束时解雇了蔡斯，福尔曼和卡梅伦则选择了辞职<ref name="error">{{cite episode | title = Human Error | series = House | credits = Writers: Kaplow, Lawrence; Moran, Thomas L. Director: Jacobs, Katie | network = Fox | airdate = 2007-05-29 | season = 3 | number = 24}}</ref>。由此豪斯不得不重新招聘几位新成员，他把人选缩小到7名医生中。制片人们起初计划招入两位全职演员，加上于第4季第5集《[[魔镜摩镜_(豪斯医生)|魔镜魔镜]]》中回归的福尔曼一起组成新的团队，最终他们决定在节目中增加3位常规角色<ref>{{cite news | first = Paula | work = Variety | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131023060532/http://variety.com/2009/scene/news/growing-cast-increases-show-s-depth-1117999268/ | url = http://variety.com/2009/scene/news/growing-cast-increases-show-s-depth-1117999268/ | title = Growing cast increases show's depth | accessdate = 2014-08-25 | last = Hendrickson | date = 2009-01-29 | archivedate = 2013-10-23 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。艾普斯、莫里森和斯宾塞的角色只是去了医院里别的部门，所以仍然有可能在节目中露面。这一期间，节目的编剧会在每一集中否决一位[[候选人|候选人]]，以此雅各布斯表示，无论是制片人还是演员自己都不知道到底最后谁能够入选，直到最后一刻方见分晓<ref name="TVG1">{{cite news | accessdate = 2014-08-25 | work = TV Guide | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140806081133/http://www.tvguide.com/news/Exclusive-House-Fired-8292.aspx | deadurl = no | url = http://www.tvguide.com/news/Exclusive-House-Fired-8292.aspx | title = Exclusive: Why House Fired "Cutthroat Bitch" | date = 2007-11-28 | author = Ausiello, Michael | archivedate = 2014-08-06 }}</ref>。到了第四季的第9集里，豪斯的新诊断小组成员终于确定，除福尔曼外，另外三位医生分别是劳伦斯·库特纳（[[卡尔·潘|卡尔·潘]]饰）<ref>{{cite news | url = http://insidetv.ew.com/2007/10/03/kal-penn-to-joi/ | title = Kal Penn joins 'House' as series regular | work = Entertainment Weekly | author = Rice, Lynette | date = 2007-10-03 | accessdate = 2014-08-25 | archivedate = 2013-10-20 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131020222207/http://insidetv.ew.com/2007/10/03/kal-penn-to-joi/ | deadurl = no }}</ref>。克里斯·陶柏（彼得·雅各布森饰）<ref name="BTVPennJacobs.">{{cite news | accessdate = 2014-08-25 | publisher = BuddyTV | url = http://www.buddytv.com/articles/house/penn-and-jacobson-talk-about-t-23615.aspx | title = Penn and Jacobson Talk About Their Journey on 'House' | date = 2008-10-15 | author = del Castillo, Valerie Anne | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140331065303/http://www.buddytv.com/articles/house/penn-and-jacobson-talk-about-t-23615.aspx | archivedate = 2014-03-31 }}</ref>和[[蕾蜜·海德利|蕾蜜·“13”·海德利]]（[[奥利维亚·王尔德|奥利维亚·王尔德]]饰）<ref>{{cite news | title = The Hot New Star of House, Olivia Wilde | work = People | date = 2007-12-11 | author = Rizzo, Monica}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url = http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/television/news/2007-10-21-house-main_N.htm | title = 'House' story line keeps the actors on edge | author = Johnson, Peter | work = USA Today | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140824133307/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/television/news/2007-10-21-house-main_N.htm | archivedate = 2014-08-24 | date = 2007-10-22 | accessdate = 2014-08-25 }}{{cite news | author = Hendrickson, Paula | url = http://variety.com/2008/scene/news/guest-spots-can-lead-to-full-time-roles-1117987166/ | title = Guest spots can lead to full-time roles | date = 2008-05-09 | work = Variety | accessdate = 2014-08-25 | archivedate = 2014-08-25 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140825072443/http://variety.com/2008/scene/news/guest-spots-can-lead-to-full-time-roles-1117987166/ | deadurl = no }}</ref>。豪斯否决的候选人中只有[[豪斯医生角色列表|安珀·沃拉基斯]]之后还有在节目中出现，她成为威尔森的女友，戏份一直持续到第四季结束<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.tvweek.com/blogs/blink/2008/06/playing_house_in_hollywood.php/ | title = Playing ''House'' in Hollywood | work = TelevisionWeek | author = Horowitz, Lisa | date = 2008-06-13 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131019155317/http://www.tvweek.com/blogs/blink/2008/06/playing_house_in_hollywood.php | accessdate = 2013-10-19 | archivedate = 2013-10-19 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>，另外还曾以豪斯幻觉的形式在第五季现身<ref name="Saviors">{{cite episode | title = Saviors | credits = Writers: Attie, Eli; Moran, Thomas L. Director: Penn, Matthew | series = House | network = Fox | airdate = 2009-04-13 | season = 5 | number = 21}}</ref>。虽然潘和王尔德比其他候选人的扮演者更有名气，但雅各布斯表示他们都通过了同样的试镜-{程}-序，并且编剧们也是基于对角色的兴趣决定让他们继续留在节目中<ref name="TVG1" />。库特纳一角于第五季第20集离开了节目，因为潘这时已成为[[白宫公众参与和政府间事务办公室|白宫公众参与和政府间事务办公室]]的工作人员<ref>{{cite news | url = http://insidetv.ew.com/2009/04/07/house-exclusive/ | title = 'House' exclusive: The shocking story behind last night's big death | work = Entertainment Weekly | date = 2009-04-07 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140305200152/http://insidetv.ew.com/2009/04/07/house-exclusive/ | author = Ausiello, Michael | accessdate = 2014-08-25 | archivedate = 2014-03-05 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。

埃德尔斯坦、艾普斯和莱纳德的合约在第7季结束时到期。出于削减成本的角度考虑，制片人希望3人同意削减片酬。艾普斯和莱纳德接受了这一安排，但埃德尔斯坦没有同意，因此2011年5月时剧组宣布她不会回归[[豪斯医生_(第八季)|第八季]]。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/lisa-edelstein-not-returning-house-189128 | title = Lisa Edelstein Isn't Returning to 'House' Next Season | last = Ng | first = Philiana | archivedate = 2012-11-14 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121114103606/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/lisa-edelstein-not-returning-house-189128 | deadurl = no | publisher = Hollywood Reporter | date = 2011-05-17 | accessdate = 2014-08-25 }}</ref>

