=== 主要角色 ===
[[File:HouseCastSeason1.jpg|thumb]]
《豪斯医生》播出期间，片头中一共出现了6名主要演员的姓名。他们扮演的医生都在节目中虚构的新泽西州普林斯顿一普兰斯堡教学医院工作<ref name="pilot" />。格瑞利·豪斯医生是医学诊断科主任，也是片名所指人物<ref>{{cite news | author = Jauhar, Sandeep | title = Magical Medicine on TV | publisher = The New York Times Company | url = http://www.nytimes.com/2005/07/19/health/19comm.html | work = The New York Times | date = 2005-07-19 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140825154631/http://www.nytimes.com/2005/07/19/health/19comm.html | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2014-08-25 | archivedate = 2014-08-25 }}</ref>。豪斯称自己拥有[[美国医学专业委员会|美国医学专业委员会]]认可的[[感染|感染]]和[[肾脏科|肾脏科]]双料诊断专长<ref name="Occam's Razor">{{cite episode | title = Occam's Razor | credits = Writer: Shore, David. Director: Singer, Bryan |series = House | network = Fox | airdate = 2004-11-30 | season = 1| number = 3}}</ref>。詹姆斯·威尔森是豪斯唯一的真正朋友，也是医院肿瘤科主任<ref name="Fidelity">{{cite episode | title = Fidelity | credits = Writer: Moran, Thomas L. Director: Spicer, Bryan | series = House | network = Fox | airdate = 2004-12-28 | season = 1 | number = 7}}</ref>。丽莎·卡蒂是[[内分泌学|内分泌科医生]]<ref name="insensitive">{{cite episode | title = Insensitive | credits = Writer: Lewis, Matthew V. Director: Sarafian, Deran | series = House | network = Fox | airdate = 2007-02-13 | season = 3 | number = 14}}</ref>，也是医学院院长和医院管理者，她是豪斯的顶头上司<ref name="Info">{{cite web | url = http://www.fox.com/house/showInfo/ | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090505213712/http://www.fox.com/house/showInfo/ | archivedate = 2009-05-05 | title = ''House''—Show Information | accessdate = 2009-05-05 | publisher = Fox.com }}</ref>。豪斯与卡蒂的关系很复杂，两人间经常含沙射影，并且伴随有很高-{程}-度的性紧张<ref>{{cite web | url = http://blogcritics.org/house-in-love-part-2-cuddy/ | title = House in Love, Part 2: Cuddy – The Thin Line Between Love and Hate | accessdate = 2014-08-26 | last = Barnett | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140825161356/http://blogcritics.org/house-in-love-part-2-cuddy/ | first = Barbara | date = 2008-12-15 | publisher = Blogcritics | archivedate = 2014-08-25 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。两人在第五季的第6集《[[快乐_(豪斯医生)|快乐]]》（{{lang|en|''Joy''}}）中首次接吻<ref>{{cite web | url = http://insidetv.ew.com/2008/09/21/lisa-edelstein/ | title = Lisa Edelstein on House-Cuddy Kiss: 'It Was a Big Moment' | accessdate = 2014-08-26 | last = Ausiello | first = Michael | date = 2008-09-21 | work = Entertainment Weekly | archivedate = 2014-08-25 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140825161611/http://insidetv.ew.com/2008/09/21/lisa-edelstein/ }}</ref>，但第五季接一来的节目中没有出现任何进一步的肉体关系，豪斯在季终时以为自己和卡蒂发生了性关系，但这只是他因维柯丁成瘾而产生的幻觉<ref name="BothSides" />。到了第六季的最后，卡蒂-{向}-豪斯表白，两人亲吻后同意试着在一起<ref>{{cite web | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140825161943/http://blogcritics.org/huddy-house-and-help-me-an/ | deadurl = no | url = http://blogcritics.org/huddy-house-and-help-me-an/ | title = Huddy, ''House'', and 'Help Me': An Interview With the Season Finale's Writers | accessdate = 2014-08-26 | last = Barnett | first = Barbara | date = 2010-05-19 | publisher = Blogcritics | archivedate = 2014-08-25 }}</ref>。整个第七季里穿插了许多有关两人关系的剧情。

豪斯最初的诊断小组包括神经科医生埃里克·福尔曼、重症监护科医生罗伯特·蔡斯和[[免疫学|免疫系统]]医生阿莉森·卡梅伦<ref name="Info" />。到了第三季第21集《家庭》时，福尔曼宣布自己决定辞职，称自己不希望变成豪斯那样的人{{#tag:ref|福尔曼还进一步-{向}-豪斯表示：“你救的人会比我多，但我宁愿自己害死的人也少些。这是我提前两星期的通知。”<ref name="Family">{{cite episode | title = Family | credits = Writer: Friedman, Liz. Director: Straiton, David | series = House | network = Fox | airdate = 2007-05-01 | season = 3 | number = 21}}</ref>|group="注"}}。豪斯在这季最后一集中告诉蔡斯，他要么能够学会自己所有的本事，要么就什么都学不到，然后把他开除出了小组。卡梅伦这时已经与蔡斯发展出恋情，她很快也辞职了<ref name="error" />。这导致豪斯的论断小组在第四季开场时只剩他一个光杆司令<ref name="Alone">{{cite episode | title = Alone | credits = Writers: Blake, Peter; Shore, David. Director: Sarafian, Deran | network = Fox | series = House | airdate = 2007-09-25 | season = 4 | number = 1}}</ref>。

卡蒂要求豪斯招入新的小组成员，豪斯为此一共考虑了40名医生<ref name="Rightstuff" />。第四季的前几集就围绕这一挑选过-{程}-展开，属[[真人实境秀|电视真人秀]]风格的淘汰竞赛<ref name="Rightstuff" />，雅各布森形容这就像“《[[幸存者|幸存者]]》的版本” <ref>{{cite news | title = Note to 'House' fans: 'Things will never be the same' on the Fox medical drama | work = USA Today | date = 2007-07-24}}</ref>。豪斯给每位候选人分配了1到40中的一个编号，把其中大部分人淘汰到只剩7人<ref name="97sec">{{cite episode | title = 97 Seconds | credits = Writers: Friend, Russel; Lerner, Garrett. Director: Platt, David | series = House | airdate = 2007-10-09 | season = 4 | number = 3 | network = Fox}}</ref>。福尔曼因在另一个医院行医时表现出类似豪斯的行为而遭解雇，于是回到了之前的老岗位上，他协助豪斯根据候选人在诊断病例时的表现作出评估<ref name="97sec" /><ref>{{cite episode | title = Guardian Angels | credits = Writer: Hoselton, David. Director: Sarafian, Deran | series = House | network = Fox | airdate = 2007-10-23 | season = 4 | number = 4}}</ref><ref name="MM">{{cite episode | title = Mirror Mirror | credits = Writer: Foster, David. Director: Platt, David | series = House | airdate = 2007-10-30 | season = 4 | number = 5 | network = Fox}}</ref>。虽然福尔曼的回归意味着小组中只剩两个空缺，但豪斯还是用计诱使卡蒂允许他聘请三位新人<ref name="Games">{{cite episode | title = Games | credits = Writer: Attie, Eli. Director: Sarafian, Deran | series = House | airdate = 2007-11-27 | season = 4 | number = 9 | network = Fox}}</ref>。他最终选择的分别是前[[整形|整形医生]]克里斯·陶柏、运动医学专家劳伦斯·库特纳和[[内科|内科医生]]蕾蜜·“13”·海德利（“13”这个绰号源于她在40位候选人中获得的编码）<ref name="Games" /><ref name="Catlin">{{cite web |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20130102134540/http://blogs.courant.com/roger_catlin_tv_eye/2007/11/house-finalists.html |url=http://blogs.courant.com/roger_catlin_tv_eye/2007/11/house-finalists.html |title='House' Finalists |date=2007-11-21 |author=Catlin, Roger |accessdate=2014-08-26 |work=Hartford Courant |archivedate=2013-01-02 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。到第四季结束时，13发现自己一直担心的事情变成了现实，她患上了无药可救的[[亨丁顿舞蹈症|亨丁顿舞蹈症]]<ref name="WH" />。

福尔曼和13在第五季第11集《给全世界的快乐》中有一个深情的吻<ref name="joytoworld" />。13起初不大情愿和福尔曼交往，但两人之后还是开始约会，并且到第五季结束时仍然在一起<ref name="BothSides" />。两人在第六季开始后不久分手。库特纳在第五季第20集《[[简单解释|简单解释]]》（{{lang|en|''Simple Explanation''}}）里死在自己的公寓，头上有枪伤。他没有留下只言片语，豪斯为此怀疑其中另有隐情，但其他角色都认为这是[[自杀|自杀]]<ref>{{cite episode | title = Simple Explanation | series = House | airdate = 2009-04-06 | season = 5 | number = 20 | network = Fox | credits = Writer: Dick, Leonard. Director: Yaitanes, Greg}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url = http://insidetv.ew.com/2009/04/07/house-exclusive/ | title = 'House' exclusive: The shocking story behind last night's big death | work = Entertainment Weekly | date = 2009-04-07 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140305200152/http://insidetv.ew.com/2009/04/07/house-exclusive/ | author = Ausiello, Michael | accessdate = 2014-08-26 | archivedate = 2014-03-05 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。

卡梅伦和蔡斯在第二季第7集《寻找元凶》中发生了[[一夜情|一夜情]]<ref name="Hunting">{{cite episode | title = Hunting | credits = Writer: Friedman, Liz. Director: Muzio, Gloria | series = House | network = Fox | airdate = 2005-11-22 | season = 2 | number = 7}}</ref>。两人在第三季中期开始经常发生性关系，但卡梅伦坚持这只是逢场作戏<ref name="insensitive" />，当蔡斯表示自己“想要更进一步”时，卡梅伦结束了两人的关系<ref name="Airborne">{{cite episode | title = Airborne | credits = Writer: Hoselton, David. Director: Keene, Elodie | series = House | network = Fox | airdate = 2007-04-10 | season = 3 | number = 18}}</ref>，但到了第三季的结尾，卡梅伦意识到自己对蔡斯有了感情，于是两人开始了正式交往<ref name="error" />。双双离开诊断小组后，两人在医院的不同部门工作，卡梅伦成为[[急症室|急症室]]的资深主治医师{{#tag:ref|根据《豪斯医生》在福克斯官方网站上页面的说法，“卡梅伦主管急诊医学部门”<ref name="Info" />。|group="注"}}，蔡斯则是外科医生<ref name="Rightstuff" />。两人在第五季第21集（库特纳自杀后的一集）《[[救世主_(豪斯医生)|救世主]]》（{{lang|en|''Saviors''}}）中[[订婚|订婚]]<ref name="Saviors" />并在季终成婚<ref>{{cite news | archivedate = 2014-03-04 | url = http://www.tvguide.com/tvshows/house/episode-24-season-5/100213 | work = TV Guide | author = Mittovich, Matt | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140304074556/http://www.tvguide.com/tvshows/house/episode-24-season-5/100213 | date = 2009-05-11 | deadurl = no | title = House Episode Recap: "Both Sides Now" | accessdate = 2014-08-26 }}</ref>。蔡斯在第六季第8集《[[团队合作_(豪斯医生)|团队合作]]》中（{{lang|en|''Teamwork''}}）重新加入豪斯的诊断小组，卡梅伦为此离开了丈夫和这所医院<ref>{{cite episode | title = Teamwork | credits = Writer: Attie, Eli. Director: Straiton, David |series = House | network = Fox | airdate = 2009-11-16 | season = 6 | number = 8}}</ref>。她之后在这季的第17集《[[锁定_(豪斯医生)|锁定]]》（{{lang|en|''Lockdown''}}）中[[友情客串|客串出镜]]<ref>{{cite episode | title = Lockdown | credits = Writers: Attie, Eli; Blake, Peter; Friend, Russel; Lerner, Garret. Director: Laurie, Hugh | series = House | network = Fox | airdate = 2010-04-12 | season = 6 | number = 17}}</ref>。

13在第7季开始后不久离开了医院，并且很长时间没有回来，也没有任何解释。卡蒂要求豪斯另请一位女医生填补13的空缺<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.tvguide.com/News/Amber-Tamblyn-House-1025203.aspx | title = Amber Tamblyn Is in the ''House'' | publisher = TV Guide | last = Keck | first = William | date = 2010-11-08 | accessdate = 2014-08-26 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-08-13 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140813113015/http://www.tvguide.com/News/Amber-Tamblyn-House-1025203.aspx }}</ref>，但之后还是亲自挑选了医科学生玛莎·麦斯特，后者在这季的第6集首度出场<ref>{{cite episode | title = Office Politics | credits = Writer: Hoffman, Seth. Director: Bookstaver, Sanford |series = House | network = Fox | airdate = 2010-11-08 | season = 7 | number = 6}}</ref>。13在这季第18集《挖掘》（{{lang|en|''The Dig''}}）回归，原来她是因给自己进入亨廷顿舞蹈症晚期的兄弟实行[[安乐死|安乐死]]而入狱服刑6个月<ref>{{cite episode | title = The Dig | credits = Writers: Hess, Sara; Hoselton, David. Director: Shakman, Matt |series = House | network = Fox | airdate = 2011-04-11 | season = 7 | number = 18}}</ref>。雅各布森和王尔德都已经像潘一样扮演核心角色，但两人的名字一直到第七季才出现在开场片段中。在此以前，他们的名字是以“次要角色”的形式在开场片段之后出现<ref>{{cite news | archivedate = 2010-09-26 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20100926182002/http://www.tvsquad.com/2008/09/25/how-about-some-new-opening-credits-for-house-already/ | url = http://www.tvsquad.com/2008/09/25/how-about-some-new-opening-credits-for-house-already | title = How About Some New Opening Credits for House Already? | publisher = TV Squad | last = Keller | first = Richard | date = 2008-09-25 | accessdate = 2010-09-26 }}</ref>。从第七季开始，雅各布森和王尔德的名字出现在开场片段，但新加入的主要演员塔布琳没有得到同样的待遇<ref>{{cite news | url = http://tv.msn.com/tv/episode/house/the-dig/ | title = Episode Info: The Dig | publisher = MSN TV | accessdate = 2014-08-26 | archivedate = 2013-12-03 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131203111311/http://tv.msn.com/tv/episode/house/the-dig/ }}</ref>。

=== 常见角色 ===
《豪斯医生》的前六季中每季都会有一到多位角色在多集节目中出现<ref name="S-L1">{{cite news | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140223112954/http://www.nj.com/entertainment/tv/index.ssf/2008/09/sepinwall_on_tv_house_season_f.html | url = http://www.nj.com/entertainment/tv/index.ssf/2008/09/sepinwall_on_tv_house_season_f.html | title = Sepinwall on TV: 'House' season five review | author = Sepinwall, Alan | date = 2008-09-16 | work = The Star-Ledger | accessdate = 2014-08-26 | archivedate = 2014-02-23 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。第一季中亿万富翁、制药公司老板[[豪斯医生角色列表|爱德华·沃格勒]]（[[齐·麦克布赖德|齐·麦克布赖德]]饰）一共出演了5集节目<ref name="NYTVogler">{{cite news | url = http://www.nytimes.com/2007/01/30/arts/television/30hous.html?pagewanted=print | work = The New York Times | author = Carter, Bill | title = ''House'', Already Strong, Gets a Boost | date = 2007-01-30 | accessdate = 2014-08-26 | publisher = The New York Times Company | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130520170425/http://www.nytimes.com/2007/01/30/arts/television/30hous.html?pagewanted=print | archivedate = 2013-05-20 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。他-{向}-普林斯顿一普兰斯堡教学医院捐款1亿美元换取董事会主席一职<ref name="control">{{cite episode | title = Control | credits = Writer: Kaplow, Lawrence. Director: Zisk, Randy | series = House | network = Fox | airdate = 2005-03-15 | season = 1 | number = 14}}</ref>。福克斯敦促剧情在节目中加入反面人物，沃格勒的出现就属于其中一次尝试。但到了包括这个角色的剧集开始播出时，节目在收视率上已经相当成功，所以这个角色之后很快就取消了<ref name="NYTVogler" />。大卫·肖表示，流氓老大的理念并不适合这个节目：“剧名叫《豪斯医生》，观众知道他绝对不可能被炒”<ref name="fullhouse" />。

豪斯的前女友[[史黛西·华纳|史黛西·华纳]]（{{lang|en|Stacy Warner}}，[[雪拉·渥德|雪拉·渥德]]饰）<ref name="honeymoon">{{cite episode | title = Honeymoon | series = House | credits = Writers: Kaplow, Lawrence; Mankiewicz, John. Director: Keller, Frederick King | airdate = 2005-05-24 | network = Fox | season = 1 | number = 22}}</ref>在第一季的最后两集亮相，还在第二季的7集节目中出现<ref name="fullhouse" />。她希望豪斯诊治自己的丈夫马克·华纳（{{lang|en|Mark Warner}}，[[库里·格拉汉姆|库里·格拉汉姆]]饰），豪斯在第一季结束时确诊他患有急性间歇性[[紫质症|紫质症]]<ref name="honeymoon" />。史黛西和豪斯再度变得亲密，但豪斯最终让她回到马克身边，这让她非常伤心<ref name="needtoknow">{{cite episode | title = Need to Know | credits = Writer: Davis, Pam. Director: Semel, David | series = House | airdate = 2006-02-07 | network = Fox | season = 2 | number = 11}}</ref>。

[[迈克尔·崔特|迈克尔·崔特]]（[[大卫·摩斯|大卫·摩斯]]饰）是一名警探，在第三季的多集节目中出场。他来到医院做检查时受到豪斯捉弄，被留在医院的一间检验室内，并且[[直肠|直肠]]中还插了一根[[温度计|温度计]]，从此崔特就较上了劲，一定要让豪斯-{向}-他道歉<ref name="FFL">{{cite episode | title = Fools for Love | series = House | credits = Writer: Blake, Peter. Director: Platt, David | network = Fox | airdate = 2006-10-31 | season = 3 | number = 5}}</ref>。豪斯拒绝道歉，于是崔特试图指控对方持有无处方的麻醉药品，强迫医生接受戒断治疗。案件闹到法庭时，卡蒂为豪斯作了[[伪证|伪证]]，案件也因此撤消。法官批评崔特对事情过于执着，还告诉豪斯自己觉得他“不配拥有这么好的朋友”，意指为他做证的卡蒂。豪斯因[[藐视法庭|藐视法庭]]被判入狱一夜，但强制性的戒断治疗也相应中止<ref name="WAD" />。

第四季的大部分常见角色都是豪斯新诊断小组的候选人<ref name="USADox">{{cite news | date = 2007-10-21 | url = http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/television/news/2007-10-21-house-cast_N.htm | title = Examine the doctors who are in the running on 'House' | author = Johnson, Peter | work = USA Today | accessdate = 2014-08-26 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121024164605/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/television/news/2007-10-21-house-cast_N.htm | archivedate = 2012-10-24 }}</ref>。除了三位最终入选的医生外，另外四位入围医生分别是[[豪斯医生角色列表|杰弗里·科尔]]（[[艾迪·盖瑟吉|艾迪·盖瑟吉]]饰）、[[流行病学|流行病学家]][[豪斯医生角色列表|特拉维斯·布伦南]]（[[安迪·科米乌|安迪·科米乌]]饰）<ref name="USADox" />、前医学院招生官员[[豪斯医生角色列表|亨利·多布森]]（[[卡门·阿尔根齐亚诺|卡门·阿尔根齐亚诺]]饰）<ref name="Rightstuff" />和介入性[[影像诊断学|放射科医生]][[豪斯医生角色列表|安珀·沃拉基斯]]（[[安妮·达德克|安妮·达德克]]饰）<ref name="Catlin" />。除沃拉基斯外，另外三人都在遭淘汰后离开了节目，沃拉基斯则与威尔森开始交往，其戏份一直持续到第四季结束<ref>{{cite news | author = Ryan, Maureen | date = 2008-03-21 | accessdate = 2014-08-25 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140708220000/http://featuresblogs.chicagotribune.com/entertainment_tv/2008/03/the-return-of-h.html | url = http://featuresblogs.chicagotribune.com/entertainment_tv/2008/03/the-return-of-h.html | title = The 'House' of love | work = Chicago Tribune | archivedate = 2014-07-08 | deadurl = no }}</ref><ref name="Frozen">{{cite episode | title = Frozen | series = House | credits = Writer: Friedman, Liz. Director: Straiton, David | network = Fox | airdate = 2008-02-03 | season = 4 | number = 11}}</ref>。第四季的剧终分[[豪斯的头|上]]、下两集，由于威尔森没空，沃拉基斯前去一家酒吧带醉酒的豪斯回家，但路上发生了车祸，她也因此遇难<ref name="WH" /><ref name="House's Head">{{cite episode | title = [[豪斯的头|House's Head]] | series = House | network = Fox | credits = Writers: Blake, Peter; Egan, Doris; Foster, David; Friend, Russel; Lerner, Garrett. Director: Yaitanes, Greg | airdate = 2008-05-12 | season = 4 | number = 15}}</ref>。此外，她还有在第五季后半部分作为豪斯的幻觉出现<ref name="Saviors" />。

第五季中有三集出现了私家侦察[[豪斯医生角色列表|卢卡斯·道格拉斯]]（[[迈克尔·温斯顿|迈克尔·温斯顿]]饰），肖创作这个角色部分是因为自己喜欢的剧集《[[回头是岸_(电视剧)|回头是岸]]》（{{lang|en|''The Rockford Files''}}）<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.nj.com/entertainment/tv/index.ssf/2008/08/more_with_house_creator_david.html | title = More With ''House'' Creator David Shore | work = The Star-Ledger | accessdate = 2014-08-26 | date = 2008-08-05 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131227085203/http://www.nj.com/entertainment/tv/index.ssf/2008/08/more_with_house_creator_david.html | archivedate = 2013-12-27 | author = Sepinwall, Alan; Fienberg, Daniel }}</ref><ref name="MRCT908">{{cite news |url=http://archives.chicagotribune.com/2008/sep/16/entertainment/chi-house-watcher-0916sep16 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5msfjraXg?url=http://archives.chicagotribune.com/2008/sep/16/entertainment/chi-house-watcher-0916sep16 |archivedate=2010-01-18 |date=2008-09-16 |author=Ryan, Maureen |title='House' overcrowded with characters |work=Chicago Tribune |accessdate=2010-01-18 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。豪斯起初聘请道格拉斯是为了查探威尔森，两人的友谊在沃拉基斯丧生后中止（之后还是合好了）。豪斯之后还请道格拉斯查探诊断小组其他成员甚至卡蒂的私生活<ref name="adverseevents">{{cite episode | title = Adverse Events | credits = Writers: Green, Carol; Paddock, Dustin. Director: Bernstein, Andrew | series = House | network = Fox | airdate = 2008-09-30 | season = 5 | number = 3}}</ref>。如果观众乐意接受这个角色，电视台有计划发展以道格拉斯为主角的[[番外|衍生剧]]<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.tvguide.com/news/exclusive-six-feet-8145.aspx | title = Exclusive: Six Feet Under Alum Ready to Play House? | work = TV Guide | author = Ausiello, Michael | date = 2008-05-15 | accessdate = 2014-08-26 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090831010330/http://www.tvguide.com/news/Exclusive-Six-Feet-8145.aspx | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2009-08-31 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.ign.com/articles/2008/05/07/spinoff-for-house | author = Goldman, Eric | date = 2008-05-07 | title = Spinoff for House? | publisher = IGN | accessdate = 2014-08-26 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121102100225/http://www.ign.com/articles/2008/05/07/spinoff-for-house | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2012-11-02 }}</ref>。2008年9月，肖-{向}-《[[娱乐周刊|娱乐周刊]]》说明了自己对这个角色的设想：“我不想再做一部医疗剧。是人们所做的选择和是非对错的本质激发我进行写作……与医生相比，私家侦探可以更容易地接近这个问题”<ref>{{cite news |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140723095215/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0%2C%2C20224783_4%2C00.html |deadurl=no |url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,20224783_4,00.html |title=''House'': Is Romance the Best Rx? |work=Entertainment Weekly |accessdate=2014-08-26 |author=Wheat, Alynda |date=2008-09-10 |archivedate=2014-07-23 }}</ref>。2009年秋的电视网络节目安排中没有包含道格拉斯一角的节目<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.tvguide.com/special/fall-preview/fall-schedule.aspx | title = Fall TV Schedule for Start of 2009–2010 Season | work = TV Guide | accessdate = 2014-08-26 | archive-date = 2009-08-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090824154636/http://www.tvguide.com/special/fall-preview/fall-schedule.aspx | dead-url = no }}</ref>，他在《豪斯医生》第六季中作为卡蒂的男友重新出现<ref>{{cite episode | title = Known Unknowns | series = House | credits = Writers: Egan, Doris; Lewis, Matthew, V. Director: Yaitanes, Greg | network = Fox | airdate = 2009-11-09 | season = 6 | number = 7}}</ref>。两人还曾订婚，但之后卡蒂意识到自己爱着豪斯而选择了分手<ref>{{cite episode | title = Help Me | series = House | credits = Writers: Blake, Peter; Friend, Russel; Lerner, Garrett. Director: Yaitanes, Greg | network = Fox | airdate = 2010-05-17 | season = 6 | number = 22}}</ref>。

== 剧集 ==
{{main|豪斯医生剧情列表}}
《豪斯医生》一共播出了8季共177集，其中第一、六、八季为22集，第二、三、五季为24集，第七季23集，第四季则因受到[[2007年－2008年美国编剧协会大罢工|2007年－2008年美国编剧协会大罢工]]的影响导致只有16集<ref name="WGAPrincetonian">{{cite news | url = http://www.dailyprincetonian.com/2008/02/29/20316/ | author = Shea, Allie | work = The Daily Princetonian | date = 2008-02-29 | title = ''House, M.D.'' co-producer offers advice | accessdate = 2009-05-23 | archivedate = 2012-03-05 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120305221514/http://www.dailyprincetonian.com/2008/02/29/20316/ | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。节目开播的第一集《试播集》于2004年11月16日首播<ref name="episode1rating">{{cite web |work=ABC Medianet |date=2004-09-23 |title=Weekly Program Rankings |archivedate=2014-08-11 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140811093105/http://abcmedianet.com/web/dnr/dispDNR.aspx?id=112304_07 |deadurl=yes |url=http://www.abcmedianet.com/web/dnr/dispDNR.aspx?id=112304_07 |accessdate=2014-08-26 }}</ref>，第一季的最后一集《蜜月》则是在2005年5月24日播出<ref name="episode22rating">{{cite web | work = ABC Medianet | date = 2005-06-01 | title = Weekly Program Rankings | url = http://abcmedianet.com/web/dnr/dispDNR.aspx?id=060105_04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140718115230/http://abcmedianet.com/web/dnr/dispDNR.aspx?id=060105_04 | deadurl = yes | accessdate = 2014-08-26 | archivedate = 2014-07-18 }}</ref>。接下来的每一季都是在上季结束的同年9月到10月初开播，次年5月播完。2012年5月21日，《豪斯医生》第八季第22集，也是整部剧集的大结局《人皆有死》播出<ref>{{cite web | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130520063636/http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2012/05/22/monday-final-ratings-dwts-agt-and-house-retrospective-adjusted-up-clash-of-the-commercials-adjusted-down/135303/ | archivedate = 2013-05-20 | url = http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2012/05/22/monday-final-ratings-dwts-agt-and-house-retrospective-adjusted-up-clash-of-the-commercials-adjusted-down/135303/ | title = Monday Final Ratings: 'DWTS', 'AGT', and 'House' Retrospective Adjusted Up; 'Clash of the Commercials' Adjusted Down | work = TV by the Numbers | last = Kondolojy | first = Amanda | date = 2012-05-22 | accessdate = 2014-08-26 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。

全部八季中在美国首播时收视率最高的是第三季，平均每集有1995万观众收看<ref name="abc07" />，其次是第四季的1764万<ref name="abc08" />；收视成绩最差的则是最后一季，平均每集吸引了869万观众<ref name="season8ratings" />。从单集节目来看，观众人数最多的则是第四季第11集《冷冻》<ref name="highestrating" />，观众人数超过2900万<ref name="Frozenratings" />，不过这主要是因为节目安排在第四十二届超级碗后播出<ref name="Frozeninterview" /><ref name="42ndsuperbowl" />。

== 反响 ==
=== 专业评价 ===
《豪斯医生》开播时所获评价以正面为主<ref name="HDT">{{cite news | author = Davies, Hugh | date = 2004-11-20 | url = http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/1477057/Dr-Laurie-has-viewers-of-US-TV-in-stitches.html | title = Dr Laurie has viewers of US TV in stitches | work = The Daily Telegraph | accessdate = 2014-08-26 | location = London | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140110004618/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/1477057/Dr-Laurie-has-viewers-of-US-TV-in-stitches.html | archivedate = 2014-01-10 | deadurl = no }}</ref>，这一期间福克斯的大部分节目都是真人秀，所以有评论认为本剧是该电视台节目中的亮点<ref name="ASNYT">{{cite news | author = Stanley, Alessandra | publisher = The New York Times Company | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130520155046/http://www.nytimes.com/2004/11/16/arts/television/16stan.html | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nytimes.com/2004/11/16/arts/television/16stan.html | date = 2004-11-16 | title = With Terminal Witticism, Even Cancer Can Be Fun | work = The New York Times | page = E5 | archivedate = 2013-05-20 | accessdate = 2014-08-26 }}</ref>。{{lang|en|[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]}}上针对第一季收集的30篇评价中有22篇好评，1篇差评，7篇褒贬不一，综合评分75，属“普遍看好”的评价<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.metacritic.com/tv/house | title = House - Season 1 Reviews | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140427043844/http://www.metacritic.com/tv/house | publisher = CBS Interactive Inc. | accessdate = 2014-08-26 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-04-27 | work = metacritic }}</ref>。《[[电视指南_(杂志)|电视指南]]》的马特·罗什（{{lang|en|Matt Roush}}）称节目是“常见医疗剧的罕见特效药”<ref>{{cite news | title = Roush Review, Doctor Feel bad; Don't ask this grouch to make house calls | author = Roush, Matt | date = 2004-11-08 | work = TV Guide | page = 1 | url = http://www.tvguide.com/roush/doctor-feelbad-dont-26867.aspx | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140321042821/http://www.tvguide.com/roush/doctor-feelbad-dont-26867.aspx | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2014-08-26 | archivedate = 2014-03-21 }}</ref>。《[[纽约每日新闻|纽约每日新闻]]》评论员大卫·比安库里（{{lang|en|David Bianculli}}）称赞了其“高水准的演技和剧本”<ref name="DBDN" />。《[[洋葱报|洋葱报]]》的《[[影音俱乐部|影音俱乐部]]》赞许这是福克斯继1996年只播映了很短时间的《[[利益_(电视剧)|利益]]》（{{lang|en|''Profit''}}）以来“最坏坏的”[[黑色幽默|黑色喜剧]]<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.avclub.com/content/node/24686 | title = A Guide for the Compulsive TV Fan | author = Gillette, Amelie; Murray, Noel & Phipps, Keith | date = 2004-11-22 | publisher = The A.V. Club | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080921222504/http://www.avclub.com/content/node/24686 | accessdate = 2008-09-21 | archivedate = 2008-09-21 }}</ref>。《[[纽约_(杂志)|纽约]]》（{{lang|en|''New York''}}）的[[约翰·伦纳德|约翰·伦纳德]]（{{lang|en|John Leonard}}）称这是“最基本也是最让人满意的医疗电视节目”<ref>{{cite news | last = Leonard | first = John | title = Scrub Par | page = 1 | work = New York | date = 2004-11-15 | url = http://nymag.com/nymetro/arts/tv/reviews/10331/ | accessdate = 2014-08-26 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140723064852/http://nymag.com/nymetro/arts/tv/reviews/10331/ | archivedate = 2014-07-23 | deadurl = no }}</ref>，《[[波士顿环球报|波士顿环球报]]》（{{lang|en|''The Boston Globe''}}）的马修·吉尔伯特（{{lang|en|Matthew Gilbert}}）则赞赏节目没有通过粉饰人物缺陷来试图缓解观众对“健康维护组织工厂”的恐惧<ref>{{cite news | author = Gilbert, Matt | date = 2004-11-16 | title = Strong Prognosis for medical show | work = The Boston Globe | page = D1 | url = http://www.boston.com/ae/tv/articles/2004/11/16/strong_prognosis_for_medical_show_house_laurie_fascinates_as_doctor_in_house/ | accessdate = 2014-08-26 | archivedate = 2014-03-21 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140321042507/http://www.boston.com/ae/tv/articles/2004/11/16/strong_prognosis_for_medical_show_house_laurie_fascinates_as_doctor_in_house/ }}</ref>。《[[综艺_(杂志)|综艺]]》的布莱恩·洛瑞（{{lang|en|Brian Lowry}}）对节目的感观略差，认为在其光鲜的包装背后仍然过于依赖情节叙事<ref>{{cite news | url = http://variety.com/2004/film/reviews/house-7-1200529558/ | title = House Review | author = Lowry, Brian | date = 2004-11-15 | work = Variety | accessdate = 2014-08-26 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140826070753/http://variety.com/2004/film/reviews/house-7-1200529558/ | archivedate = 2014-08-26 }}</ref>。蒂姆·-{古}-德曼（{{lang|en|Tim Goodman}}）在《[[旧金山纪事报|旧金山纪事报]]》上表示剧集表现平淡，缺乏原创性<ref name="sfgate-review">{{cite news | author = Goodman, Tim | date = 2004-11-15 | title = Network meddling by Fox execs starts the deathwatch for 'House' | work = San Francisco Chronicle | accessdate = 2014-08-26 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131001211755/http://www.sfgate.com/entertainment/article/Network-meddling-by-Fox-execs-starts-the-2635158.php | archivedate = 2013-10-01 | url = http://www.sfgate.com/entertainment/article/Network-meddling-by-Fox-execs-starts-the-2635158.php }}</ref>。
