格瑞利·豪斯一角获得了普遍好评<ref name="HDT" /><ref>{{cite news | title = House, Humanity Is Overrated | publisher = PopMatters | author = Fuchs, Cynthia | date = 2004-11-22 | url = http://www.popmatters.com/tv/reviews/h/house-2004.shtml | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090210075604/http://www.popmatters.com/tv/reviews/h/house-2004.shtml | deadurl = yes | accessdate = 2009-02-10 | archivedate = 2009-02-10 }}</ref>。《[[华盛顿邮报|华盛顿邮报]]》的[[汤姆·谢尔斯|汤姆·谢尔斯]]（{{lang|en|Tom Shales}}）称这是“多年来电视上最激动人心的新主角”<ref name="TSWP">{{cite news | author = Shales, Tom | date = 2004-11-16 | title = 'House': Watching Is the Best Medicine | work = The Washington Post | url = http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/articles/A53025-2004Nov15.html | accessdate = 2014-08-26 | archive-date = 2018-08-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180809112434/http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/articles/A53025-2004Nov15.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。《[[匹兹堡邮报|匹兹堡邮报]]》（{{lang|en|''Pittsburgh Post-Gazette''}}）的罗布·欧文（{{lang|en|Rob Owen}}）发现这个人物“没同情心到令人着迷（的-{程}-度）”<ref name="Owen">{{cite news | url = http://www.post-gazette.com/pg/04319/410715-237.stm | title = TV Review: Hugh Laurie makes 'House' worth a visit | author = Owen, Rob | date = 2004-11-14 | work = Pittsburgh Post-Gazette | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120118054239/http://www.post-gazette.com/pg/04319/410715-237.stm | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2012-01-18 | accessdate = 2014-08-26 }}</ref>。有影评人拿豪斯和虚构侦探[[尼诺·沃尔夫|尼诺·沃尔夫]]（{{lang|en|Nero Wolfe}}）<ref name="USAtoday-pilot-recap">{{cite news | author = Bianco, Robert | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140320190628/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/television/reviews/2004-11-15-house_x.htm | accessdate = 2014-08-26 | url = http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/television/reviews/2004-11-15-house_x.htm | title = There's a doctor worth watching in 'House' | work = USA Today | date = 2004-11-16 | archivedate = 2014-03-20 | deadurl = no }}</ref>、[[赫丘勒·白罗|赫丘勒·白罗]]以及[[艾德里安·蒙克|艾德里安·蒙克]]（{{lang|en|Adrian Monk}}）做比较<ref>{{cite news | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140224052438/http://www.seattlepi.com/ae/tv/article/Fox-s-medical-drama-House-is-a-welcome-1159563.php | url = http://www.seattlepi.com/ae/tv/article/Fox-s-medical-drama-House-is-a-welcome-1159563.php | title = Fox's medical drama 'House' is a welcome transfusion of quality programming | author = McFarland, Melanie | date = 2004-11-16 | work = Seattle Post-Intelligencer | accessdate = 2014-08-26 | archivedate = 2014-02-24 | deadurl = no }}</ref>，同样拿来对比的还有《[[实习医生风云|实习医生风云]]》中的[[佩里·考克斯|佩里·考克斯]]（{{lang|en|Perry Cox}}），他也是位脾性-{古}-怪的医生<ref name="ASNYT" /><ref name="Owen" />。有研究发现豪斯和《[[风流军医俏护士_(电视剧)|风流军医俏护士]]》中的鹰眼·皮尔斯（{{lang|en|Hawkeye Pierce}}）医生有强烈的血缘关系<ref name="Wilson-2007" />{{rp|76-78}}。劳瑞的演出获得了广泛好评<ref name="PopMatters" /><ref name="USAtoday-pilot-recap" /><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,831962,00.html |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140517122957/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0%2C%2C831962%2C00.html |title=House (2004) |author=Flynn, Gillian |work=Entertainment Weekly |date=2004-12-03 |accessdate=2014-08-26 |deadurl=no |archivedate=2014-05-17 }}</ref>。《旧金山纪事报》的-{古}-德曼称他“大概是观看《豪斯医生》的唯一理由”<ref name="sfgate-review" />。《[[每日邮报|每日邮报]]》的加布里埃尔·唐纳利（{{lang|en|Gabrielle Donnelly}}）认为，劳瑞复杂的个性让他成为这个角色的完美人选<ref name="Dailymail" />。

节目中的首批配角也获得了较为正面的评价，谢尔斯在《华盛顿邮报》称节目拥有“一流的群体演出”<ref name="TSWP" />。《电视指南》<ref>{{cite news |last=Fretts |first=Bruce |title=Cheers: A House Divided |work=TV Guide |date=2008-09-17 |archivedate=2008-10-24 |deadurl=yes |accessdate=2008-10-24 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081024012328/http://community.tvguide.com/blog-entry/TVGuide-Editors-Blog/Cheers-38-Jeers/Robert-Sean-Leonard/800046864 |url=http://community.tvguide.com/blog-entry/TVGuide-Editors-Blog/Cheers-38-Jeers/Robert-Sean-Leonard/800046864 }}</ref>、《娱乐周刊》和《今日美国》都认为莱纳德对威尔森医生的诠释值得[[艾美奖|艾美奖]]的肯定<ref>{{cite news | title = Spoilery Video: 'House' Cast on Thirteen's Bisexuality, Wilson's Grief and More! | work = Entertainment Weekly | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130528104411/http://insidetv.ew.com/2008/07/15/spoilery-video-2/ | archivedate = 2013-05-28 | url = http://insidetv.ew.com/2008/07/15/spoilery-video-2/ | author = Ausiello, Michael | date = 2008-06-15 | deadurl = yes | accessdate = 2014-08-26 }}</ref><ref name="Bianco">{{cite news | title = The finale word on the TV season | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121023104623/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/television/news/2008-05-22-tv-finales_n.htm?loc=interstitialskip | date = 2008-01-07 | work = USA Today | accessdate = 2012-10-23 | author = Bianco, Robert | deadurl = no | url = http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/television/news/2008-05-22-tv-finales_n.htm?loc=interstitialskip | archivedate = 2012-10-23 }}</ref>。《纽约每日新闻》的比安库里表示很高兴能看到埃德尔斯坦“终于获得了应得的共同主演角色”<ref name="DBDN" />。自由撰稿评论家丹尼尔·法恩伯格（{{lang|en|Daniel Fienberg}}）对莱纳德和埃德尔斯坦的演技没得到更多认同而感到失望<ref>{{cite web |author=Fienberg, Daniel |accessdate=2014-08-26 |date=2007-09-24 |url=http://www.baltimoresun.com/topic/zap-review-house_s4premiere,0,2573501.story |archivedate=2012-10-22 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121022111751/http://www.baltimoresun.com/topic/zap-review-house_s4premiere%2C0%2C2573501.story |title=TV Review: 'House' Fourth Season Premiere |work=Baltimore Sun |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

节目第四季的重大转变所获评价褒贬不一。{{lang|en|DVD Talk}}的小托德·道格拉斯（{{lang|en|Todd Douglass Jr.}}）认为“有了新成员进驻后，《豪斯医生》也有了更加精力充沛的感觉”，他还称赞“第五季的设定堪称辉煌”<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.dvdtalk.com/reviews/34531/house-md-season-four/ | title = House, M.D. – Season Four | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131004120450/http://www.dvdtalk.com/reviews/34531/house-md-season-four/ | deadurl = no | author = Douglass Jr., Todd | publisher = DVD Talk | date = 2008-08-19 | accessdate = 2014-08-26 | archivedate = 2013-10-04 }}</ref>。《[[明星纪事报|明星纪事报]]》（{{lang|en|''The Star-Ledger''}}）的艾伦·塞平沃尔（{{lang|en|Alan Sepinwall}}） 写道：“（节目规模的）扩大、大量的工作面试让编剧有机会重新给节目注入活力，充分发挥劳瑞的喜剧天赋”<ref name="S-L1" />。而《[[洛杉矶时报|洛杉矶时报]]》的玛丽·麦克纳马拉（{{lang|en|Mary McNamara}}）则表达了不同看法：“演员越来越多，故事越来越分散而且不平衡，直到一堆伟大的演员都被迫站在一旁看着休·劳瑞纯粹依靠自己的意志力来支撑整个节目”<ref name="MMLAT">{{cite news | title = 'Grey's,' 'Private Practice,' 'House' get healthy | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130226044217/http://articles.latimes.com/2008/oct/07/entertainment/et-medicalshows7 | url = http://articles.latimes.com/2008/oct/07/entertainment/et-medicalshows7 | author = McNamara, Mary | date = 2008-10-07 | work = Los Angeles Times | accessdate = 2014-08-26 | archivedate = 2013-02-26 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。《今日美国》的罗伯特·比安科（{{lang|en|Robert Bianco}}）为这季的结局喝彩：“不是常说好戏在后头么。编剧们用这美妙且令人心碎的两小时……挽救了这季看起来已经有些过于发散、人满为患、有些过于雄心勃勃到产生不良后果的节目”<ref name="Bianco" />。

与前几季相比，《豪斯医生》的第五季获得的评价更加正面。{{lang|en|Metacritic}}上收集的10份评论中有9份好评，无差评，1份褒贬不一，综合评分77<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.metacritic.com/tv/house/season-5 | title = House - Season 5 Reviews | publisher = CBS Interactive Inc. | accessdate = 2014-08-26 | work = metacritic | archivedate = 2014-04-27 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140427043820/http://www.metacritic.com/tv/house/season-5 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。而[[烂番茄|烂番茄]]上收集的9份评论则全部给出了“新鲜”的正面评价，“新鲜度”达100%，[[加权平均数|平均得分]]8.1（最高10分）<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.rottentomatoes.com/tv/house/s05/ | title = House - Season 5 Reviews | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140225205015/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/tv/house/s05/ | work = Rotten Tomatoes | deadurl = no | publisher = Flixster | accessdate = 2014-08-26 | archivedate = 2014-02-25 }}</ref>。《今日美国》称赞了劳瑞的表演和第四季结局产生的反响，称节目“结转上季的辉煌结局，豪斯坚定地走上前方。如果你有个演员拥有休·劳瑞的戏路、深度和魅力，让他掌控舞台中央绝对是明智之举，特别是当你想要创作一个故事来发掘这样的角色以及他主要人际关系的时候”<ref>{{cite web | title = House moves squarely into the limelight in season opener | url = http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/television/reviews/2008-09-15-house-preview_N.htm?csp=34 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140221065550/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/television/reviews/2008-09-15-house-preview_N.htm?csp=34 | author = Robert Bianco | publisher = USA Today | accessdate = 2014-08-26 | archivedate = 2014-02-21 }}</ref>。《[[纽约每日新闻|纽约每日新闻]]》指出：“节目更注重那些我们在意的关系，还暗示其中可能还会有一些新的关系，并且将数目控制在合理范围内，所以并不完全依赖于晦涩的医学奥秘来担负起全剧戏剧性需要的包袱”，文章还进一步指出，“这一季的[[预后|预后]]似乎会比上季预示的更好”<ref>{{cite web | accessdate = 2014-08-26 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140223130446/http://www.nydailynews.com/entertainment/tv-movies/repairs-fixed-house-article-1.324577 | url = http://www.nydailynews.com/entertainment/tv-movies/repairs-fixed-house-article-1.324577 | title = Repairs seem to have fixed 'House' | author = David Hinckley | publisher = New York Daily News | archivedate = 2014-02-23 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。《洛杉矶时报》的玛丽·麦克纳马拉强调了演员的表演，特别称赞迈克尔·温斯顿（{{lang|en|Michael Weston}}）饰演的私家侦探卢卡斯·道格拉斯是对节目“令人愉快的补充”。她在总结中认为，新的一季可能会与观众的期待有所差异，虽不致差别太大，但已经有相当-{程}-度的不同<ref name="MMLAT" />。不过，《[[芝加哥论坛报|芝加哥论坛报]]》的莫琳·瑞安（{{lang|en|Maureen Ryan}}）不喜欢温斯顿的角色，称他是“不受欢迎的旁枝……让人讨厌的小人物”<ref name="CTseason5">{{cite news | title = Thirteen + 'House' = wrong number | author = Ryan, Maureen | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140222004050/http://featuresblogs.chicagotribune.com/entertainment_tv/2008/12/house-laurie.html | url = http://featuresblogs.chicagotribune.com/entertainment_tv/2008/12/house-laurie.html | date = 2008-12-11 | work = Chicago Tribune | accessdate = 2014-02-22 | archivedate = 2014-02-22 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。她还进一步表示，“《豪斯医生》曾是电视上最好的节目，但却已严重脱离了预定方-{向}-。”《[[星期日泰晤士报|星期日泰晤士报]]》觉得节目已经“失去了幽默感”<ref>{{cite news | url = http://entertainment.timesonline.co.uk/tol/arts_and_entertainment/tv_and_radio/article6424140.ece | title = Hugh Laurie must hate House | author = Gill, A. A. | date = 2009-06-07 | work = The Sunday Times | accessdate = 2014-08-26 | location = London | archive-date = 2020-05-30 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200530191208/https://www.the-tls.co.uk/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。此外，对于13以及她和福尔曼关系的关注也特别受到了批评<ref name="S-L1" /><ref>{{cite news |title=Breaking up is hard to do, even with TV shows |author= |date=2009-04-04 |work=Ottawa Citizen |publisher=Canwest News Service |accessdate=2014-08-26 |deadurl=yes |archivedate=2014-02-21 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140221215944/http://www2.canada.com/ottawacitizen/news/insideout/story.html?id=44d41edb-6039-4628-bc73-11830f2b467d&p=2 |url=http://www2.canada.com/ottawacitizen/news/insideout/story.html?id=44d41edb-6039-4628-bc73-11830f2b467d&p=2 }}</ref>。

节目到达尾声时，《娱乐周刊》的史蒂芬·通（{{lang|en|Steven Tong}}）表示，《豪斯医生》在最后一季里变成了相当多愁善感的节目<ref name="Tucker">{{cite web | last = Tucker | first = Ken | title = 'House' series finale review: All's well that ends musically | url = http://watching-tv.ew.com/2012/05/21/house-series-finale-hugh-laurie-robert-sean-leonard/ | work = Ken Tucker's TV | publisher = Entertainment Weekly | accessdate = 2014-08-26 | date = 2012-05-21 | archive-date = 2012-05-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120525051646/http://watching-tv.ew.com/2012/05/21/house-series-finale-hugh-laurie-robert-sean-leonard/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。玛格丽特·莱昂斯（{{lang|en|Margaret Lyons}}）在《纽约》杂志网站上写道，《豪斯医生》已经超出了医疗剧或人物剧或其它任何一部剧集，成为对痛苦的复杂冥想。不过她还认为，“开明的[[犬儒主义|犬儒主义]]”和“痛苦的混乱和虚无”之间还是有一条界线，“随着节目的进展，其戏剧性的火炬变得黯淡，而痛苦的火炬却燃烧得更加明亮”<ref name="Vulture">{{cite web | last = Lyons | first = Margaret | title = House Series Finale: The Show Was a Meditation on Misery | archivedate = 2014-02-21 | url = http://www.vulture.com/2012/05/house-series-finale-hugh-laurie.html | work = Vulture blog | publisher = New York Magazine | accessdate = 2014-08-26 | date = 2012-05-21 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140221165727/http://www.vulture.com/2012/05/house-series-finale-hugh-laurie.html }}</ref>。艾伦·塞平沃尔表示：“中间几季的反复和不当处理最终断绝了我对豪斯个人奋斗拥有的任何情感联系”<ref name="SepFinale" />。

《豪斯医生》在《娱乐周刊》评选的“新电视经典”中名列第62位<ref>{{cite web |title=The New Classics: TV |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140716041112/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0%2C%2C20207339%2C00.html |deadurl=no |archivedate=2014-07-16 |url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,20207339,00.html |work=Entertainment Weekly |accessdate=2014-08-26 |date=2007-06-18 }}</ref>。此外，节目还在2002至2012年的{{lang|en|[[互联网电影数据库|IMDB.com]] Pro}}评选中拥有第二高的电视节目评分<ref>{{cite web | archivedate = 2014-04-22 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140422190007/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/brad-pitt-johnny-depp-dark-knight-lost-imdb-top-10-284912 | date = 2012-01-25 | work = The Hollywood Reporter | author = Schillaci, Sophie A. | deadurl = no | url = http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/brad-pitt-johnny-depp-dark-knight-lost-imdb-top-10-284912 | title = Johnny Depp, 'The Dark Knight,' 'Lost' Named to IMDb's Top 10 of the Last Decade | accessdate = 2014-08-26 }}</ref>。

