=== 美国收视成绩 ===
《豪斯医生》的第一季在美国播出时的收视率可以在所有电视剧中排到第24位，并且在所有最受女性观众欢迎的黄金时段节目中名列第9位<ref name="badmood">{{cite news |last=Winters |first=Rebecca |date=2005-09-04 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140815211951/http://content.time.com/time/magazine/article/0%2C9171%2C1101308%2C00.html |title=Doctor Is in... a Bad Mood |work=Time |url=http://content.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,1101308,00.html |issn=0040-781X |accessdate=2014-08-26 |archivedate=2014-08-15 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。接下来的三季节目安排在广受欢迎的《[[美国偶像|美国偶像]]》之后播出<ref name="Challen" />{{rp|43-44}}，每一季都在所有年龄段观众中收获了前十名的收视率。从[[尼尔森收视率|尼尔森收视率]]的数据看，《豪斯医生》的第三季成绩最好，平均每集吸引了1940万观众<ref name="Ratingsseason3">{{cite web | title = 2006–07 primetime wrap | archivedate = 2012-01-02 | url = http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/hr/content_display/television/features/e3ifbfdd1bcb53266ad8d9a71cad261604f | publisher = Nielsen Business Media | date = 2007-05-25 | accessdate = 2012-01-02 | work = The Hollywood Reporter | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120102063804/http://www1.hollywoodreporter.com/hr/content_display/television/features/e3ifbfdd1bcb53266ad8d9a71cad261604f | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。据雅各布斯表示，剧组对节目能够吸引这么多观众感到惊喜<ref name="Challen" />{{rp|44}}。《豪斯医生》的第五季平均每集吸引了1200万观众，总体排名下滑到第19位，但仍然是福克斯除《美国偶然》外最受欢迎的节目<ref name="TVratings09">{{cite web | title = ''American Idol, Dancing With The Stars'' Top Average Viewership For 2008–9 Season | publisher = TV by the Numbers | accessdate = 2014-08-26 | url = http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2009/05/27/american-idol-dancing-with-the-stars-top-average-viewership-for-2008-9-season/19519/ | last = Gorman | first = Bill | date = 2009-05-27 | archivedate = 2013-10-26 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131026010727/http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2009/05/27/american-idol-dancing-with-the-stars-top-average-viewership-for-2008-9-season/19519/ }}</ref>。

第四季第11集《[[冷冻_(豪斯医生)|冷冻]]》（{{lang|en|''Frozen''}}）在[[第四十二届超级碗|第四十二届超级碗]]后播出<ref name="Frozeninterview">{{cite web | author = Kubicek, John | date = 2007-10-09 | url = http://www.buddytv.com/articles/house/exclusive-interview-house-star-12201.aspx | title = Exclusive Interview: 'House' Star Robert Sean Leonard | publisher = BuddyTV | accessdate = 2014-08-26 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140320172956/http://www.buddytv.com/articles/house/exclusive-interview-house-star-12201.aspx | archivedate = 2014-03-20 }}</ref><ref name="42ndsuperbowl">{{cite news | date = 2008-02-04 | accessdate = 2014-08-26 | first = John | url = http://www.buddytv.com/articles/house/house-postsuper-bowl-episode-f-16318.aspx | title = House: Post-Super Bowl Episode "Frozen" Recap | publisher = BuddyTV | last = Kubicek | archivedate = 2014-03-31 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140331064120/http://www.buddytv.com/articles/house/house-postsuper-bowl-episode-f-16318.aspx }}</ref>，是《豪斯医生》收视率最高的一集<ref name="highestrating">{{cite news | archivedate = 2014-07-20 | deadurl = no | url = http://featuresblogs.chicagotribune.com/entertainment_tv/2008/02/house-post-supe.html | title = ''House'' post-Super Bowl episode to air again, plus ''Bones'' news | work = Chicago Tribune | date = 2008-02-05 | author = Ryan, Maureen | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140720133752/http://featuresblogs.chicagotribune.com/entertainment_tv/2008/02/house-post-supe.html | accessdate = 2014-08-26 }}</ref>，吸收了超过2900万观众观看<ref name="Frozenratings">{{cite news | date = 2008-02-05 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130510194116/http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2008/02/05/top-fox-primetime-shows-jan-28-feb-3/2571/ | url = http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2008/02/05/top-fox-primetime-shows-jan-28-feb-3/2571/ | title = Top Fox Primetime Shows, Jan 28 – Feb 3 | publisher = TV by the Numbers | author = Gorman, Bill | deadurl = yes | accessdate = 2014-08-26 | archivedate = 2013-05-10 }}</ref>。《豪斯医生》在这个星期的所有电视节目中收视排名第三，仅次于超级碗比赛和[[第四十二届超级碗|赛后演出]]，超过了《美国偶像》<ref>{{cite web | last = Gorman | first = Bill | date = 2008-02-24 | url = http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2008/02/24/top-timeshifted-broadcast-shows-jan-28-feb-3/2722/ | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131113225246/http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2008/02/24/top-timeshifted-broadcast-shows-jan-28-feb-3/2722/ | title = Top Time-Shifted Broadcast Shows, January 28 – February 3 | work = TV by the Numbers | accessdate = 2014-08-26 | archivedate = 2013-11-13 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。下表中将列出《豪斯医生》各季在美国电视市场的收视排名，按平均每集观众人数计算。美国每年的[[电视联播网|电视联播网]]季节从9月开始，次年5月结束。

