temmys_noms.php | title = The 61st Primetime Emmy Awards and 2009 Creative Arts Emmy Awards Nominees are.. | publisher = Academy of Television Arts & Sciences | archivedate = 2009-11-14 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20091114174651/http://cdn.emmys.tv/awards/2009ptemmys/61stemmys_noms.php }}</ref>。大卫·肖凭第一季第21集《[[三个故事_(豪斯医生)|三个故事]]》（{{lang|en|''Three Stories''}}）获2005年黄金时段艾美奖的最佳编剧奖<ref name="05emmynoms" /><ref name="ap-emmy-winners2005">{{cite news | agency = Associated Press | title = Full list of Emmy winners | work = The Sydney Morning Herald | date = 2005-09-19 | accessdate = 2014-08-26 | url = http://www.smh.com.au/news/tv--radio/full-list-of-emmy-winners/2005/09/19/1126981983610.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140307173615/http://www.smh.com.au/news/tv--radio/full-list-of-emmy-winners/2005/09/19/1126981983610.html | archivedate = 2014-03-07 | dead-url = no }}</ref>和2006年的[[人道奖|人道奖]]<ref name="Huminwon">{{cite web | url = http://www.humanitasprize.org/pdf/2006%20HUMANITAS%20Winners.pdf | format = PDF | title = 32nd Humanitas prize winners announced | date = 2006-06-28 | accessdate = 2009-04-24 | publisher = Humanitas Prize | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090424071224/http://www.humanitasprize.org/pdf/2006%20HUMANITAS%20Winners.pdf | archivedate = 2009-04-24 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。导演格雷格·艾坦尼斯因执导《[[豪斯的头|豪斯的头]]》获2008年黄金时段艾美奖正剧剧集最佳导演奖<ref name="08emmywinners">{{cite press release | title = Academy of Television Arts and Sciences 60th Primetime Emmy Awards | publisher = Academy of Television Arts & Sciences | date = 2008-09-21 | url = http://cdn.emmys.tv/downloads/2008/PTE60winners_pressrel.pdf | format = PDF | accessdate = 2009-03-19 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090319195301/http://cdn.emmys.tv/downloads/2008/PTE60winners_pressrel.pdf | archivedate = 2009-03-19 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。

