eign Press Association |publisher=Hollywood Foreign Press Association |accessdate=2014-08-26 |archivedate=2014-03-16 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140316063620/http://www.hfpa.org/browse/?param=%2Fyear%2F2007 |deadurl=no }}</ref>，[[第66届金球奖|第二年]]再度提名同一奖项，但均未能胜出<ref>{{cite news | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131212111429/http://www.buddytv.com/articles/true-blood/golden-globes-true-bloodmad-me-25190.aspx?pollid=3001406&answer=3004694#poll3001406 | publisher = BuddyTV | archivedate = 2013-12-12 | url = http://www.buddytv.com/articles/true-blood/golden-globes-true-bloodmad-me-25190.aspx?pollid=3001406&answer=3004694#poll3001406 | title = Golden Globes: 'True Blood','Mad Men' Among Nominees | author = Williams, Don | date = 2008-12-11 | accessdate = 2014-08-26 | df =  }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.goldenglobes.org/nominations/year/2008 |title=The 66th Annual Golden Globe Awards (2009) |accessdate=2014-08-26 |publisher=Hollywood Foreign Press Association |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140201165949/http://www.hfpa.org/browse/?param=%2Fyear%2F2008 |archivedate=2014-02-01 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

