-6-1117993380/ | title = Czech Republic: Opening the digital floodgates | author = Nadler, John | work = Variety | date = 2008-10-03 | accessdate = 2014-08-26 | archivedate = 2014-08-26 }}</ref>。剧集在[[法国|法国]]<ref>{{cite news | title = France falls in love with Hugh Laurie, 'the greatest seducer in the world' | author = Davies, Lizzy | work = Observer | date = 2009-04-12 | accessdate = 2014-08-26 | location = London | url = http://www.theguardian.com/books/2009/apr/12/france-hugh-laurie-house-novel | archivedate = 2013-10-21 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131021013927/http://www.theguardian.com/books/2009/apr/12/france-hugh-laurie-house-novel | deadurl = no }}</ref>、[[西班牙|西班牙]]<ref>{{cite news | title = Hugh Laurie: the house-master gets quizzed | author = Thompson, Emma | work = Interview |date=2008-06-07}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title = Spain: The good, the bad, and the digital | author = Wilson, Douglas | work = Variety | date = 2008-10-03 | accessdate = 2014-08-26 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130731004516/http://variety.com/2008/scene/markets-festivals/spain-15-1117993391/ | url = http://variety.com/2008/scene/markets-festivals/spain-15-1117993391/ | archivedate = 2013-07-31 }}</ref>、[[瑞典|瑞典]]和[[荷兰|荷兰]]都很受欢迎<ref>{{cite news | url = http://variety.com/2009/scene/news/house-connects-across-the-globe-1117999267/ | title = 'House' connects across the globe | accessdate = 2014-08-26 | last = Levine | first = Stuart | date = 2009-01-29 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140826141009/http://variety.com/2009/scene/news/house-connects-across-the-globe-1117999267/ | work = Variety | archivedate = 2014-08-26 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。《豪斯医生》的前四季通过[[英国第五台|第五台]]在[[英国|英国]]首播，[[天空第一台|天空第一台]]获得了节目第五季开始的首播权<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.theguardian.com/media/2009/apr/20/sky-house-hugh-laurie | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131111223739/http://www.theguardian.com/media/2009/apr/20/sky-house-hugh-laurie | title = Sky1 to Air Hugh Laurie Drama House | work = The Guardian | author = Holmwood, Leigh | date = 2009-04-20 | accessdate = 2014-08-26 | location = London | archivedate = 2013-11-11 }}</ref>。节目的英语原版还有在[[澳大利亚|澳大利亚]]<ref>{{cite web | url = http://ten.com.au/house.htm | title = TV Shows: House, M.D | publisher = Network Ten | accessdate = 2012-10-05 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121005092837/http://ten.com.au/house.htm | archivedate = 2012-10-05 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>、[[新西兰|新西兰]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.tv3.co.nz/Drama/House/tabid/128/Default.aspx?showid=13056 |publisher=TV3 |title=House, M.D |accessdate=2014-08-26 |archivedate=2014-03-31 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140331073224/http://www.tv3.co.nz/Drama/House/tabid/128/Default.aspx?showid=13056 }}</ref>和[[爱尔兰|爱尔兰]]播映<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.tv3.ie/shows.php?request=house | title = House | publisher = TV3 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121119173708/http://www.tv3.ie/shows.php?request=house | deadurl = yes | accessdate = 2012-11-19 | archivedate = 2012-11-19 }}</ref>。

