2007年4月23日，{{lang|en|Housecharitytees.com}}网站开始限时拍卖印有“{{lang|en|Everybody Lies}}”（意为“人皆说谎”）字样的{{lang|en|T}}恤用作慈善事业。销售收入将令[[美国心理疾病联盟|美国心理疾病联盟]]受益<ref>{{cite web | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130620025601/http://www.tvfodder.com/house/archives/2007/04/house_items_for_sale_and_chari.shtml | url = http://www.tvfodder.com/house/archives/2007/04/house_items_for_sale_and_chari.shtml | title = "House" Items for Sale and Charity Auction | accessdate = 2014-08-26 | date = 2007-04-23 | publisher = TV Fodder | archivedate = 2013-06-20 }}</ref>。《豪斯医生》的演员和剧组成员还会定期参加美国心理疾病联盟的募捐活动，并为该组织拍摄了多幅广告，曾刊登在《[[17_(美國雜誌)|17]]》和《[[滚石_(杂志)|滚石]]》杂志上。节目已经为慈善事业筹集了数十万美元善款。雅各布斯表示，希望能够通过与美国心理疾病联盟的合作，去掉“一些疾病的污名”<ref>{{cite news | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140826150911/http://variety.com/2009/scene/news/nami-benefits-from-house-support-1117999266/ | url = http://variety.com/2009/scene/news/nami-benefits-from-house-support-1117999266/ | title = NAMI benefits from 'House' support | author = Weisman, Jon | work = Variety | date = 2009-01-29 | accessdate = 2014-08-26 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-08-26 }}</ref>。

{{lang|en|[[Nettwerk|Nettwerk]]}}于2007年9月18日发行了《豪斯医生电视原声带》（{{lang|en|''House M.D. Original Television Soundtrack''}}）唱片<ref>{{cite news | title = Get Ready for Some 'House' Music | author = Claustro, Lisa | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121019154345/http://www.buddytv.com/articles/house/get-ready-for-some-house-music-10307.aspx | url = http://www.buddytv.com/articles/house/get-ready-for-some-house-music-10307.aspx | date = 2007-09-04 | publisher = BuddyTV | accessdate = 2014-08-26 | archivedate = 2012-10-19 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。其中包括《豪斯医生》中出现过歌曲的完整版本，还包括特别为节目录制且从未发行过的歌曲<ref name="IGNnews">{{cite news | title = House Gets A Soundtrack | url = http://uk.ign.com/articles/2007/08/14/house-gets-a-soundtrack | publisher = IGN Music | date = 2007-08-14 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140826151841/http://www.ign.com/articles/2007/08/14/house-gets-a-soundtrack | accessdate = 2014-08-26 | author = Staff | archivedate = 2014-08-26 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。2008年，西班牙语游戏公司{{lang|en|Exelweiss}}）根据节目设计了一款[[手机游戏|手机游戏]]，发行有[[西班牙语|西班牙语]]和英语两种版本<ref name="EX">{{cite web | url = http://www.exelweiss.com/desarrollo/videojuegos/movil/java/house.php | title = House, the mobile game based on the TV series | publisher = Exelweiss | accessdate = 2014-08-26 | archivedate = 2014-08-07 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140807023822/http://www.exelweiss.com/desarrollo/videojuegos/movil/java/house.php }}</ref>。

2009年6月，游戏开发商{{lang|en|Legacy Interactive}}宣布获得环球影业数字平台集团的许可协议，开发一款根据剧集制作的[[电子游戏|电子游戏]]，玩家将成为豪斯诊断小组的一员，研究5个不同寻常的医学病例<ref>{{cite web | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20100102165005/http://legacygames.com/news/press_release/2009/legacy_announces_house_and_murder_she_wrote | title = Companies Announce House M.D. for the PC and Nintendo DS and Murder, She Wrote for the PC | publisher = Legacy Interactive | date = 2009-06-02 | accessdate = 2010-01-02 | archivedate = 2010-01-02 | deadurl = yes | url = http://www.legacygames.com/news/press_release/2009/legacy_announces_house_and_murder_she_wrote }}</ref>。这款游戏于2010年5月发行，其中还包括一款迷你游戏，玩家要从迷宫般的餐馆中把一个巨大的[[三明治|三明治]]带到豪斯医生的办公室，一路上还要防范饥饿医生的袭击。这款游戏评价不佳，影音俱乐部对其评分为{{lang|en|[[成绩|F]]}}<ref name="AVC">{{cite web | url = http://www.avclub.com/article/house-md-41188 | title = House M.D | publisher = The A.V. Club | first = David | last = Wolinsky | date = 2010-05-17 | accessdate = 2014-08-26 | archivedate = 2013-11-23 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131123194306/http://www.avclub.com/article/house-md-41188 | deadurl = no }}</ref>，但{{lang|en|Legacy}}还是在2010年8月对游戏进行了更新<ref name="AVC" />。

